(14, 'Importance of Reading for Better Writing', '<h1>Importance of Reading for Better Writing</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>It is obvious that reading plays an essential role for the better writing. There are so many programs for children and adults that motivate the reading skills for many years. Some community programs such as &ldquo;The Rays&rdquo; provides more knowledge about the importance of reading practices. In many areas, people are more focus to develop the strong writing skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Basically, reading allow to observe, explore and know new things. By reading, you can easily analyze the situation what actually the writer described. For example, the writer has many skills to organize the information and structure the paragraph in different ways. The writer enhances the interest of readers or wrap up all the ideas and provide the satisfying conclusion. The more you will read, the more you will realize the effectiveness of reading. Reading helps to observe the critiques and improve own writing skills. Reading provides a better chance and sense what effective writing looks like. Even you don&rsquo;t have any idea to be a professional writer, and you may know the writing techniques and skill. These skills and techniques factors make you successful in landing and keeping a job. The well-writing style might equal like &ldquo;money in the bank&rdquo; for you. But unfortunately, several companies complain that their staff do not write well, despite that they have widespread writing skills and courses from many colleges. The best thing is that the professional experts and writers are more agreeable to improve their writing skills. They mainly focus on reading rather than write. As there are the lot of people who want to improve their writing skills, both personally and professionally. They follow a key ingredient of reading books and articles to get the achievement. Many social groups and bloggers write well to gain the readers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are two things generally that writers are mostly recommended to other people who want to improve their writing skills: the more writing and the more reading. Writing more is an obvious thing and practice makes perfect writers. But it is also considered that writing in a vacuum that will not do as must as good. While, reading exposes different styles, different forms, the different voice and different genres of writing. Significantly, it discloses the people to write in a better way and help to improve skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The importance of reading describes the initial learning stage at school. It is very easy to think that we have got to sort out and we do not need to work to improve the skills anymore. Many people think that they do not need for reading exercise. Reading is considered to be a fun activity. It is really easy to make a habit of reading on daily basis. To start reading, it is vital to select a genre, an author or a topic in which you feel very active and energize. It helps to make effective reading styles. The people read new updated articles and blog post on a daily basis. It is like a true story. Sometimes people share reading biographies. Some like fictions and non-fiction stories to read. Everyone has own style of reading that makes more comfortable.&nbsp; Reading involves two things, Comprehension and memory. Comprehension of the material of the subject and memory to recollect the reading material. Both components are the major process of learning. In fact, there are the lot of studies and researches that have suggested that reading improves the overall writing skills as compared to learn separately such as grammar, language and structure. Writing involves a lot of reading, either it includes small articles, large articles or business presentation.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Reading helps to expose different writing styles</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you are a business person or you are a professional writer, you leading level determines your writing style. Many English authors who are not expert in writing but they made reading into practices, and they improve their writing skills. They develop their special writing that makes more interest to readers. Writing is an art that could be express everywhere, either in newspaper, article, blog or magazine. There are many journals available in several fields. Reading habits make the best exposure to different writing styles. The writers make their own creative writing styles that distinguished from other writers. They have their own scenarios and events to express their ideas to other.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Reading improves concentration</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Writing a project is the difficult task. It needs more concentration. It is the one when writers require lots of researches. But, regular reading in a day helps to improve the ability of concentration. You have to do practice to get more attention and concentration on reading. With the help of reading practice, the concentrations on project writing will also become increase.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>The Connection of Reading and Writing </strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>There is a deep connection between reading and writing. It is basically inter-connected with each other. As the teacher teaches their languages so that they can become a better communicator under the selective disciplines. Reading is the dynamic role for the growth and it has the reciprocal relationship with writing. Generally, it is agreed that the development of effective learning and better reading habits improve the students&rsquo; skills and writing abilities. Due to the fact that reading with a disciplined manner helps the students to be professional writers in any field. &nbsp;Reading also accelerates the writing process especially to discover the new ideas and thinking process. That is why reading plays an important role to improve and affirms the cognitive skills. But in general, it is independent, boundless, creative, original and critical thinking skills. The way to use reading that intentionally improves your writing skills read those writers or authors that made you more admire. Select the most favorite paragraph, and then start writing according to it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the end, the most important thing to remember, never gets stresses over reading. Always read for the fun, gain new experiences and enhance the knowledge.</p>', 1, 2, 'published', 'importance-of-reading-for-better-writing', 1, 1, 2, '2018-09-28 13:53:04', '2018-09-28 13:53:59', NULL),
(15, 'Important Leadership Skills Needed in Student Life', '<h1>Important Leadership Skills Needed in Student Life</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The implication of leadership skills far becomes much important for a student due to the reason of participation in several group work and activities. At several steps of an education life, a student used to indulge in a variety of teamwork tasks, whereby it needs to prove its leadership skills. For example, it depends on the leader as the way to unite its team members, assign them roles as per the abilities, and take back work through them, along with positive outcomes. Such an experience of a student could better provide confidence to act in future professional and personal life too. There are several key leadership characteristics that needs grow up in student life and evaluate the outcomes. For example, the sense of responsibility develops a good and positive characteristic in a student, whereby a student ensures the accomplishment of its daily homework or any assignment, on time. Otherwise, a teacher may not become happy and a student would far behind as compared to its group mates or fellows, in the way of achieving not only good grades, but appreciation or recognition as well. In the way of it, it could better facilitate and convey the similar characteristics to others.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Another important leadership skill that needs develop in student life, refers to the confidence of students, help them to face the different cultural people, interact and seek several different new skills and knowledge through them. It helps gain knowledge about several new subjects of interest, its implications, curriculum, and the overall topics to be covered by a student. Besides, a confident leadership could set and guide the team members in any teamwork task, and define the mission and vision to them. A confident leadership would then be a strong supporter of the team members, and ensure to motivate them. In associated with it, network building activity could better enhance in a student life, prove to be an effective leader. Through the skill, an individual student could better interact with its team members, ask them and support them, and could better continue the group network in the future too. Network development activities could far better be helpful for a student to achieve success in its education life, like in the way of accomplishment of several research projects, conduct interviews through professional personnel or discuss with the tutor about the progress or performance. Thus, a student far better feel confident in its academic and professional life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Problem-solving skill is another important skill that consistently develops in a student and essential to become a team leader. A good leader is the one that could resolve all of the problems, occur in a group, like time management deficiency, accomplishment of different steps of a project, and the overall achievement of a project. in the academic life of a student, it may faced several issues, like students faced a deficiency of capital to complete a project, time management, and carry out the entire work, equally and with due responsibility, from the side of all of the members. Inspiration is another important factor or leadership trait that has to develop in student life. In this way, people or the other fellows want to work along, for a long time. it gets inspire through the sacrifices made in a group work, discussion and interaction, and the overall implication tactic applied to resolve several difficulties, faced in a group. The factors of inspiration used to attract the other fellows to work along with, and take guidance and help through the leader. The level of communication and confidence help gain the leadership position and guide others, accordingly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here, it is important to discuss the characteristics of a student leader in the light of the book Leadership: Research Findings, Practice, and Skills, whereby it is highlighted that a student has to posses several characteristics to become a leader. It includes authenticity, assertiveness, extraversion, enthusiasm, humility and trustworthiness. For example, being a self-confident leader, a student could better accomplish a challenging goal, even in its personal life as well as academic life. A student could develop trust, via aligning words, actions, and the overall attitude. Also, authenticity develops via matching goals and values, along with the personality traits. An extraversion student leader better be able to interact with other people, and enjoy all tasks, with people. In the way of it, it could better facilitate the accomplishment of tasks, along with enthusiasm and passion. Assertiveness leads determine the concerns of different people, and resolve different difficulties, and complexities, faced by each member in a team and find out solutions, accordingly. It requires a leader to interact with people, via verbal or non-verbal communication, along with care, respect, and dignity, as per the age, level of knowledge, or the overall otherwise. Thus, self-esteem, self-assertiveness and the other such characteristics are important to develop by a student leader.</p>', 1, 2, 'published', 'important-leadership-skills-needed-in-student-life', 1, 1, 2, '2018-09-28 13:55:18', '2018-09-28 13:55:31', NULL),
(16, 'Managing your Studies and Taking Time Out for Olympic Events', '<h1>Managing your Studies and Taking Time Out for Olympic Events</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The Olympic Games are to demonstrate the sportspeople the incredible discrimination and commitment. It takes years in the training of the people. It makes an early start with a willingness to sacrifice one&#39;s social life altogether. Nowadays, many people are not able to show their strengths that is why the Olympians are considered as such special people. The Olympians are such inspirations for the people all around the world. For a student, it seems hard to manage the studies and taking time out for the Olympian events. The student must visualize success accordingly. A simple tactic that is according to the top athletes must be planned. The person should make a picture of planning and deal for the event that is helpful in studies and games both. Whenever a student works towards the goal, smells and feels it, then it will be useful to bring out the scene in life for his achievements and desire more tangible. He feels like a champion when he will start to act like a champion. The Olympians must be motivated in keeping the continuous training for just one competition. The student has to manage it accordingly. With the studies, he must focus on the practice no matter how much it is difficult but he must provide a positive impact and must love it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Both summer and winter Olympics provides many sports that are highly visible like soccer, football, and cricket. The students are getting opportunities to watch the professional athletes in sports that are helpful in participating and focusing on some games. For students, it is beneficial to get involved in many sports activities. It provided physical strength to increase the mental power. The outdoor sports like football, cricket, volleyball, hockey, running, etc. are helpful for improving physical health and mental fitness. The games and strength are considered as two sides of the coins. The student must involve in the sports activities in order to get more strength with physical exercise. The student who is interested in sports is bringing the right career by participating at national and international levels. Playing games is helpful to strengthen the immune system, to maintain physical coordination, to enhance body strength, and to improve mental power. Discipline is also relevant to the life of the students. It provides imbibed in them from the starting. It is helpful for the students in signing up for the sports and learning the importance of discipline. It follows the rules and listening of the coaches in order to create and maintain the control.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>From the social standpoint, the Olympics is a powerful tool that brings the people together and creates a sense of community. It develops the connection and bonds between the people from all lifestyles. As for reading and writing involved in mental stress. The mind then hungers for relief. Reading and writing also participate in physical strain. The physique of a student needs extra fuel. Regular participation in Olympics Games is helpful to make the body fit at the same time give the relief that is required. The present arrangement of games and sports in the life of a student is most unsatisfactory. The student is participating in the Olympics Games in fact that to take part in the games. The training for different branches of games and sports are given in a scientific way under the excellent coach, and the sustainability is provided to all departments of sports and games. It is determined by the abilities and interest of the students. The inclusion of Olympics Games in the curriculum of studies is essential. It is necessary for modern times. The schools must provide value to the students who are participating in different Olympics Games.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the competing demands that are placed on the spare time of the students, it is necessary for them to plan and know the schedule. The students must manage the school time, game time, and practice time accordingly. It is helpful to get time on the calendar and determine the actual homework time and study time. Therefore, it is essential to get focus on time management. The more efficiently a student spend the time, is more helpful in achieving the goals. The student must focus on the tips for time management with sports and studies. Some suggestions are:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Prioritise the plan:</strong> The student must prioritize the idea of interests. If he sees the benefit in the sports, then it is better to watch TV or do other work later on.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Remember the purpose: </strong>The student must remember the use of studies and playing sports. It will provide a sense of accomplishment in achieving the goals.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Do not ignore warning signs:</strong> The students must create some warning signs and workings according to it like not to sleep at the time of the study. Make a schedule to provide better performance in both studies and sports.</li>\r\n</ul>', 1, 2, 'published', 'managing-your-studies-and-taking-time-out-for-olympic-events', 1, 1, 2, '2018-09-28 14:01:22', '2018-09-28 14:01:33', NULL),
(17, 'Problems College Students Face and How to overcome them', '<h1>Problems College Students Face and How to overcome them</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The students are facing various issues that are commonly experienced in their college life as in their studies. Play, socializing, living etc. The challenges are to be identified, described, and suggested for further management. While spending time at college, the students experience different things. The college students are dealing with various problems during the time. What one of the challenges students face in their academic life is lack of providing efforts than the school. The students seem to offer much attention towards the time management. Therefore, the students much make a schedule for educating and doing other work in order to make their minds fresh and bright. The students must manage it in the ways to release their academic stress and seek guidance from the experts for their study habits. The students are also facing problems of homesickness for those who are living away from their parents and family. They are feeling the loneliness that is affecting their studies and academic life. Therefore, the students who are living far from their parents must visit them after some days or on some educational vacations. They can also send emails and cards to their family and ask them to do it the same. It is helpful to be in touch with other and reduce the feelings of homesickness.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Students also face social problems in their college life like in making the new friend while entering the college. It is essential for the student to establish connections and spend time with the classmates and roommates for building the community. It is helpful if any conflict or challenges arise. However, sometimes-social relations become a distraction. The students must have limited relationships with other people that will not distract from their studies and academic life. The best way to overcome is to spend more the spare time on some coffee shop or a mall. It is also better to talk to the neighbours and visit local parks. But, always prioritize the time of the study.&nbsp; The students are also seemed to be involved in some part-time jobs in order to afford high tuition fees. These types of activities are not providing them enough sleep. Therefore, without proper rest, the students are getting physical and mental health problems. In order to overcome this issue, the student must focus on deciding what is essential. It is necessary to provide priority and schedule the events, games, meeting, social events, and studies according to it. The students must also aware of the rules while searching for the job. As some posts are only for students that will not affect their study time and health.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What the food serves in the college is not like home food or not cooked like home cooking. The students can gain weight in their college life while overeating starch and junk food. The students are also facing issues regarding their health and complaining about it. The students must select the menu that is good for their health. They must seek for the place that offers clean and healthy food to them. The food is not like Mom or dad cooking or not exactly like home food cooks the menu, but it will not affect their health and help them to enjoy their college life. The students must also dress differently in college. The students are exploring their identity and want to look differently during their vacations and to go home. There are many choices for the students to complete their projects and tasks. There are many clubs, organizations, activities, courses, lectures, and different concerns to decide what to go on. The students must have the judicious active involvement that is helpful to them in making the better use of their time and increases the quality of their work. The students must be fresh and must balance before committing in any group or activity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Students at the college also face problems of change in behaviour. They must have to be mature in order to make responsible choices and engage them in the most constructive behaviours. The students can plan parties that are important for them to enjoy their time. But, it is essential to keep track of the friends in order to check that they are in the safe place. The students might also get difficulty in sleep. As very few college students can get a regular sleep of over eight hours that, they need daily. It is one of the biggest challenges for the college student. There is no easy cure for that but; the student must try to get adequate sleep and to figure out the ways that distract them while sleeping or when deciding to sleep. It is helpful by exercise moderately every day, take enough and healthy meal, avoids unhealthy activities, and avoids naps that mess up the body&#39;s natural sleep.</p>', 1, 2, 'published', 'problems-college-students-face-and-how-to-overcome-them', 1, 1, 2, '2018-09-28 14:03:25', '2018-09-28 14:03:37', NULL),
(18, 'Role of Mother in Setting the Educational Platform', '<h1>Role of Mother in Setting the Educational Platform</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>A mother plays a key role in the early childhood development program, whereby it does not teaches a child as the way to talk, interact, and play but enhance and improve the behavior of a child. It is, therefore, Mother&nbsp;Child&nbsp;Education&nbsp;Program could run as a home-based program and it could carry out within 24-hours a day. Thus, it could better empower a child when a mother teaches, as well as give confidence to learn and seek more new things and aspects. It is the mother that recognized several surrounding things and objects to a child, like different animals, flowers, plants, or the other different non-living objects. It has once said that an educated mother generates and fosters an educated nation. A major reason is the improvement of behavior of a child that sets out a distinctive parameter as what is wrong and what is right. There is an important fact discovered that when a mother educates a child then it could help enhance cognitive, emotional, motor and social skill development. Even across several remote areas, like in Columbia, where there is a lack of accessibility towards education, if mothers are educated, they used to teach their child, up to a significant level. Across different areas, where there is a lack of availability to get access to proper education to a child or deficiency of transportation, there could run low-cost home-based programs for mothers. In this way, mothers could provide proper education to their child at their home.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A proper education provided to a child, from a mother, assist in nurturing the mindset of a child, helps develop a healthy environment in a home. It then promotes self-sustaining growth and changes in the lifestyle and living pattern of a child. There exists a fact that in the development of a child, both parents play a key role. However, mother specifically plays its part due to spending a significant portion of time with the child. It is, therefore, a mother could better keep control and monitor the whole-day activities of its child, thus develop tactics to improve it. It is the responsibility of a mother to set out separate timings for its child, to play, read and learn as well as for the other useful activities. Otherwise, it would create deficiencies in a child as unable to manage its time, in the long run, and faced so many physical and psychological problems. For example, children usually faced anxiety or stress due to the inability to complete their course on time, thus become unable to achieve good grades. Also, those mothers who do not pay attention to the education of their child, such the children may move towards any negative direction, like involve in several small to high level of criminal activities, or distract the whole society through their irresponsible attitude. It is, therefore, mothers have to pay a significant attention to deal with all of the circumstances, faced by a child within the whole life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A mother does not only play role in setting out an education platform for a child, at home, but at the other places too. For example, a mother gives confidence to a child to go to school, interact with fellows, and teachers, and move ahead towards success. Otherwise, if the home environment of a child does not god and healthy then it continuously distracts the education, in school too. Such the child would not feel confident, as well as unable to learn, efficiently, due to unable to develop concentration or avoid through the mental distraction. It is important for a mother to understand the linkage between the home and school environment of a child. A child learns better about the language, culture or beliefs and attitude applied in a society or community, through its mother. It is the mother that provides knowledge about the norms and behavior, applied in a specific community or those essential to live in a society. in this way, as a child grows, all those values and beliefs gets transform, and the child better able to evaluate and judge it, accordingly. Thus, such an education also becomes necessary for a child, to spend its life and adopt far better practices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It could say that the education platform set out by a mother better facilitates a child to learn a wide variety of skills, improve behavioral competencies, and help in the overall growth of life, in the positive direction. It is important to set out home-based setting for the education of a child to get close to its education life, as well as personal and social life too. As a result, a child learns several different new skills and raise constructive characteristics that could not help in education, but personal, professional and social life too help in making life successful.</p>', 1, 2, 'published', 'role-of-mother-in-setting-the-educational-platform', 1, 1, 3, '2018-09-28 14:06:24', '2018-09-28 14:07:03', NULL),
(19, 'Students Making the Most Out of Social Media for Learning', '<h1>Students Making the Most Out of Social Media for Learning</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>One of the reasons for social media to become famous is by allowing people to personalise their ways and experiences by interacting with the internet. The students are using tools like Facebook, Twitter, and Instagram that are almost exclusively used to take the break from academics. The social media is increasing its advantage of study tools, especially for the tech-savvy students. From the starting of the elementary schools to the university levels, social media is playing a lead role to empower parents, students, and teacher. It is useful for sharing information and building a community among different people. Statistics show that more than 95% of the students are having internet access and using at least one social media network. Some of the students are using it for entertainment purpose, but some are using it to learn different things and make it useful in their education. It is helpful for promoting the valuable activities and learning processes. Students are using it for finding summer internships, improving a success story an winning of the student-loan battle in order to collaborate on international projects that make everything better. The students use social media in order to seek changes in the education system and learn from those changes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whenever it comes to social media, the schools are adopting and tending towards different positions. In general, consensus it is useful to get sharing information and organizing the school tasks. At the same time, social media is also blaming the lack of attention in students during classes. It is the increasing trend to adopt the social media activities for education and learning. Social media is beneficial in the educational process that does not have a stop on the student-teacher relationship. Many benefits are to be extracted from the use of social networking at the higher level as well. The principals and administrators are also finding ways to integrate social media. It is helpful in sharing the school news via social networks, holding online meetings with the parents, and starting any fundraising for different projects. The people of school, college, and universities are encouraged to make the use of technology for the students and parent communication through social media networking. The benefits are obvious, starting, and making the relationship healthier by changing the way of students&#39; learning. Every social media channel have its characteristics and rules with the variety of benefits for the classroom. The students are inevitable to use social media apps having the array of benefits for the school.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The students are integrating the use of social media in their education and learning process by controlling in a specific way. The teachers and lecturers are educating by using these platforms that increase the engagements and interactions. The learning management systems like Moodle and Blackboard have now become immensely popular in the education system from recent years that means to distribute lecture notes and other course information. The porter and students upload information and assignments in order to check the plagiarism, and that is an excellent way to communicate with the lecturers and with each other. The social media platform allows the students to get easy integration with the help of different applications like Twitter, Facebook, or LinkedIn. Social networking tools are affording the students and institutions use multiple opportunities in order to improve the learning and advanced educational methods. The networks are helpful in incorporating the plug-in to enable the sharing and interactions. The students are getting benefits from the online sources and tutorials that are shared by the social networks. Social media provides a valuable knowledge that is to be gained on various topics or issues for study purposes. For educational institutions, it is crucial to help and create a better student training strategies and shaping the students&#39; culture.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The education system has tackled the students in the learning that is related to the issues to improve the education schemes. It is beneficial for the institutions to use popular learning management systems with the integration of social media to best reach and effect through a network. The social learning benefits live conferencing systems, webinar capabilities, share group reviews, blogs, etc. The social networking interacts with the advances in the education system and becomes the number one means for solving educational problems. The essential benefits of social networking are beneficial for network building and helpful tool to access the learning and produce a pleasant process. The digital marketing qualification inspires the learners to know about the role of social media in education. It is useful in leading the various social media and marketing job paths. Thus, in this age of social media, teachers are not considered as the centre of learning as the students are. The education is supporting the students in developing a robust learning network. It requires the understanding of how social media words to connect&nbsp; it safely and responsibly.</p>', 1, 2, 'published', 'students-making-the-most-out-of-social-media-for-learning', 1, 1, 2, '2018-09-28 14:09:47', '2018-09-28 14:10:00', NULL),
(20, 'Technology changing the landscape of education', '<h1><strong>Technology changing the landscape of education</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Education level worldwide is ever-changing, particularly within the world through rapid advancement and improvement in technology. The new methods and process of techniques are highly available because the way through which the tutors teach and students are being taught through the important changes as well. It has been found that the basics of education and core principles remain the same however the method and process of teaching have been changed. The new generation is linked with the technology more as compared to students in the past. It has been determined that the three core advancements in specific have been done more to effectively changes the landscape of the education. These changes mainly include online teaching, learning software and massive open online courses. Moreover, all of these are effectively serve the purpose of engaging or connecting the students and developing more effective and flexible education system.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It has been argued that despite the advancement in the education level the students have increased their competencies and skills. However, the education based on advanced technology becomes expensive.&nbsp; It has been reported that as far as independence of the student is concerned, it is stated that the online training effectively provides more studying methods and the freedom to learn from different sources. Furthermore, the online education is currently nothing such as degree mills of the past. It is mainly the diversity of the learning which is different and unique in various cases as the curriculum itself reflects the physical equivalent. It has been reported that the traditional education system has been described through the passing of the information or knowledge by the content expert to the beginner learners. The overall process of the instruction that has altered marginally, especially through the invention of the effectively printing the press and highly industrialised approach has changed in the last few years. On the other hand, the entire mechanism of the education has remained similar.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;There is the number of arguments related to the ineffectiveness of the traditional models within the education in the information age, especially in the higher education. Moreover, despite the slow adaptation of the advanced education in the modern information age the increase of the online courses and imminent death of the lecture are the two important examples of the changing or transforming landscape of the education. Moreover, at the same time, most of the teachers in different educational institute believe that the increasing level of technology in the education will mainly support them in delivering the best content through effective way. The educational institutes are mainly forced to adopt the new technologies to meet the future educational requirements.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the current educational context, the majority of the students in the classroom mainly complete their task or assignments effectively. For instance, if the assignment is to be completed on the MS word or to write the particular research paper on various tools the use of technology help to increase the efficiency of the context written in the assignment. The use of digital technology within the education and in 21st-century learning process has become highly advanced and quite fashionable. The educational institutes and different schools around that would have the multiple sources to effectively integrate the various digital tools that are eager to perform so. The digital tools and devices in education are not only the beginning. There are still intimations of the higher changes to come in the educational context to improve the level of education in the current environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It has been found that effectively connecting the digital tools within the educational paradigm will able to significantly deliver the innovation in the needs of the students and society. The students in this era mostly need the advanced learning process to improve their competency and meet the future job and industry requirements. The technology in the education sector has effectively supported the learners to enhance their learning capabilities, effectively manage the time, and effectively collect the data from online sources. Traditionally the students required more time in collecting or searching data from libraries. Through the advancement in technology, the students can have access to the online library from which they will collect the number of books just through few clicks. This, in turn, helps them to collect high-quality material without investing time and money.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The education level of the current or latest generations of the teachers has one important twist as they are being taught how to use the technology in the education. The latest generations effectively understand and know that how to use the technology in various effective and useful means. Technology is supporting students in making the jobs simpler and easier. It also supports them to have assessed the information of the students as the overall objectively is possible. Moreover, it also supports students to keep the entire class or students to engage effectively.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It has been reported that the everyday life mainly comprises the technology. It has been reported that technology has been used as the important source for improving the quality of the education. The recent studies reflected that when technology is connected or aligned into classroom students can effectively able to get the benefit as a great deal. Therefore the technology is required to connect within the classroom for the students.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The current education system provides different opportunities to learners as compared to previous years. The education level mainly differs from the traditional education process. In the last fifty years, the technology has drastically changed that different affected sectors, business and education level. Now educational institutes are mainly focused on adopting advanced technology to encourage the individual to develop and improve the learning capabilities. There is the number of improvement that has been brought into the education world that includes the videos, computers and other digital devices. The online classes and communication with the tutor is also another new trend that provides the effective opportunity for the students to communicate with the teachers through the online portal. In addition, the technology mainly comprises the information presentation technologies which comprise the various interactive whiteboard and the Smart boards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There is the number of benefits that students have received from the use of technology in education such as an increased level of knowledge and information. However, the main problem that is mainly faced by teachers is that they might not understand or consider how to effectively use the technology that is available to them. The technology is important in the current educational context as it helps individual to increase the performance both in academic and professional level. The role of technology within the field of the education is the four-fold it is comprised as the part of the entire curriculum as the effective instructional delivery process, as the ways of aiding different instruction and the as significant tool to improve the overall learning process. The technology within education has mainly gone from the passive to reactive. Education is important in academic and corporate settings. The formal education process or training is applied to support employees to perform the similar task in different ways. The technology in education encourages the skills development process among individuals. Furthermore, the effective use of the technology in an organization mainly supports individuals and students to retain and understand the concepts superior.</p>', 1, 2, 'published', 'technology-changing-the-landscape-of-education', 1, 1, 2, '2018-09-28 14:12:06', '2018-09-28 14:12:22', NULL),
(21, 'Tips for International Students to Survive Abroad', '<h1>Tips for International Students to Survive Abroad</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The International education significantly provides a rewarding and enriching experience for whole life. The international student learns a lot while studying in abroad, knowledge of new cultures. There are many ways in which a student can easily survive.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Wisely spend and save money</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>The money is the major stress factor for all students. International education is an expensive part for those students who study abroad. The student should know about all the expenses save money as much as can. Managing money is the challenge for every student.&nbsp; Particularly, many students feel that wise spending means they are very poor. It is not true, spending wisely makes more manageable about money.&nbsp; The best plan of budgeting is to overcome all the expenses. Every student should make a diary in which he or she could write down all the cost such as food cost, books, and the material of study, phone bills and internet. He should also note down other entertaining stuff such as the movie, fun with friends, concert, ticket and trips etc. The student who studies abroad should analyze all the monthly expenses where should make the proper cut-down and save more money. The student should use promotional and discount coupons at marts, supermarkets and in theatres. Savings can help any hurdles and sickness. It makes a student&rsquo;s life easy.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Join societies</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>The international students should join the societies and student&rsquo;s groups for fun and make new friends. It helps to get new learning and modern languages. There is the wide range of societies that every student can join. It is not just bounded for any ethnic or subjective societies. The student will be able to get new opportunities that had never get before. Making friends helps to gain new hobbies. An international student should be proactive and do not make any limited committees and societies. It is very efficient to build your career.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Stress and Mental Health</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>It is very important for every student to know about his mental health.&nbsp; Should be aware of stress and it is an avoidable factor. There are several factors of stress that includes, depressions, anxieties, cultural shock and homesickness etc. It mostly happens during exams, coursework pressure, deadlines, competition with classmates and family problems. The students who are facing these kinds of stress must highlight the importance of mental health. The student should develop a clear plan and set some goals to achieve. Select any hobby the help to take out of this stress. The student should also try to connect with the family at any time, make the little conversation. In this way, the student could feel more comfortable, relax and energized. The student can also consult with the support staff of the university and share all the difficulties and problems with them. The support staff can help to encounter serious health issues. The university should be able to offer medical referral and appropriate counselling.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Culture Shock</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>The cultural shock experience can impair the homesickness, especially if the customs and culture dramatically impact on the study, the student will not easily cope up these cultural shocks. The student will face disappointment, lost and disoriented at the initial stage of international education.&nbsp; The student does not need to get panic and behave strongly. There are some ways and limitation that impacts on the cultural shock. The student should strongly know the basics of the native language. English is the main language that every student feel more confident about it. To avoid cultural shocks, the student should get involved in clubs, societies and other activities. It is the great way to engage with people and understand the nature of people.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Making Friends</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>It is very necessary to make new friends in the international country. Making a friend helps to remember the students in any situation. Study at abroad gives an opportunity to the student to meet different people with diverse background and culture. The student must build the social circle, allow people to know, share and discuss any problems and issues. Making friends not only to form connections for joy, but friends will remain side by side during any trouble. The student should embrace the differences and experience new things in life.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Personal Safety</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Safety and security is another essential part for international students. The student must know the surroundings and situations for personal safety. The student should be confident and stay within boundaries if he found any trouble. Make connections with people so that they can help in any trouble and unsafe situation.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Stay foolish and stay hungry, study is still most important mission</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>The main objective of many international students, they are much focused on their studies. They set the plan and get good results in the exams. Many successful people are highly engaged in their studies. They do not focus on any extracurricular activities. Staying hungry makes more ambitious. Frequently, students who have aimed to get good results, they have a high tendency to relax and comfortable because they work very hard to attain goals. Mostly international students have lots of work to do. They always focus on their studies.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Become a local-transport expert</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>It is very tempting to travel in cabs during while travelling to new places. But, sometimes it is very expensive. There are so many students who are studying abroad, use public transports and local trains during travel. They save their money and do not spend too much amount on travelling. Many international students do not pay the cost of the taxpayer. They mostly get transportation discounts at many places which are very feasible for them. Many places offer travel packages to international students such as Railcards and coachcards. They are usually available when students have the short time to stay for studies.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Eat and drink healthy and affordably</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Mostly international students try local restaurants in any country. They do not spend too much amount on any meal. Student makes them limited and focuses on the study. The student should try to cook itself and consider to save the money.</p>', 1, 2, 'published', 'tips-for-international-students-to-survive-abroad', 1, 1, 2, '2018-09-28 14:13:51', '2018-09-28 14:14:07', NULL);
