(59, 'How to Approach Your Essay Writing Task?', '<h1>How to Approach Your Essay Writing Task?</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Essay writing could not consider an easy task, specifically when a student has a limited timeframe and has to include all of the relevant details. To write an essay, it has to use the appropriate set of keywords and thus moves along with the analysis. Through the keywords, a reader could better develop an image and or perception about the subject study of an essay. Otherwise, if not identify any keyword, it would make far difficult for a reader to find out the aim of the composition, and its significance. Hence, the effectiveness of an essay lies in the keywords, identified by the writer. Along with the analysis, it has to provide a reflection or develop a learning scenario for the readers, achieve through after conducting the essay. It is important to give the reflection experience so that readers could extract out the key idea through the theme. It could better understand the purpose of an essay, the design to be facilitated or spread, and the overall scenario predicts the situation or trend, identify in the piece. Otherwise, it would make far difficult for a reader to evaluate the key idea, and reflector matches personal opinion or perception as with the writer&rsquo;s opinion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the light of the Kathy Livingston&#39;s Guide, there has identified a seven-step procedure to write an essay. It starts with the selection or allocation of a topic develops an outline, write down the thesis statement, the body part, and set out the introductory part of the essay. It then raised the conclusion, obtained after conducting the research. Hence, the outcome also demonstrates the key facet acquired through the study as well as the reflective learning experience achieve through the essay. Through such an organized piece, divided into parts, a reader could better facilitate by reading the most important parts. In detail, the topic of choice has to identify by the essay writer itself or assign by any level-headed person, like the tutor, etc. After defining a range of ideas, it has to link up or develop a connection between the different approaches, so that it could find out the overall purpose of the essay, and the flow of reading would not discontinue in the middle. To make an essay as far more effective, it may identify the thesis statement, in which the main point of the essay along with the topic, reveal to the readers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thus, overall, an essay has to develop in such a way that it contains all of the relevant facts and figures about the subject. All those facts and figures have to valid, so that it could attract the readers, accordingly. Hence, it needs to illustrate the current trends, and recognize the significance of the study. An essay writer could better attract more and more readers through its essay if it presents strong arguments, facts, statistics, and demonstrate the current scenario, relevant to the study. Also, it could identify the appropriate future path to the readers so that it could find out the clue to continue to discover new facts and figures.</p>', 1, 6, 'published', 'how-to-approach-your-essay-writing-task-1', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 14:44:18', '2018-10-01 14:44:18', NULL),
(60, 'There Are Two Ways for Writing an Essay Successfully', '<h1>There Are Two Ways for Writing an Essay Successfully</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>An essay may write as a discursive essay in which a particular subject, issue or topic usually analyze regarding the objectives, discussed sequentially. In such a composition, the problem might do have a high level of controversy. Instead, it depends on the capabilities of an essay writer as to describe a balanced opinion or adopt a balanced approach to demonstrate both sides of a fact. It must not favor or take aside, but it has to represent augments as side by side. As a result, it could present a stable structure of an essay that could attract its readers. The style of a discursive essay is formal, as well as not personal, thus identify a coherent set of the structure of ideas. Each paragraph of a piece starts with a new topic sentence. Also, each issue used to discuss along with a new section. It would become comfortable and convenient for the readers to read out the fundamental ideas of an essay; it does not have enough time. For the specific purpose, it needs read out the details, discuss along with a topic sentence in each paragraph. A reader after combining the different vital ideas could make up the purpose of the essay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There is another way to present an essay, i.e. the argumentative structure, in which the focus of an essay writer is to identify and describe the pros and cons on a particular subject, issue, or scenario. On the one hand, the purpose of an argumentative essay is to add up to the existing learning experience of readers. However, another aim of the essay is to influence or persuade a reader towards one single opinion, person, object, or scenario. In short, it might be possible that argumentative essay may change the perspective of a reader, and lead it in a new direction or towards any issue. An argumentative essay usually follows a general format, and structure. At first, a writer needs to mention the initial thesis statement that would define the argumentative viewpoint of the author. To prove the argument, an essay writer would then present strong and valid facts and figures. However, to describe an argument, it usually identified both sides of a fact, but consistently favors a single one.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a whole, there has to use keywords or demonstrate the linkage relationship of key ideas, in each essay, either discursive or argumentative. Side by side, there has to be a proper use of link verbs to adjoin the different ideas, identified in each section. It could use impersonal constructive sentences or passive voice sentences as well, if necessary. Also, to add up value into an essay, it could use idiomatic sentences, expressive language, and devise to use short sentences so that a reader could better read the essay and attract through it, and suggest others as well. Besides, there must not use any colloquial or slang language that may distract the flow of essay, as informal in its approach.</p>', 1, 6, 'published', 'there-are-two-ways-for-writing-an-essay-successfully', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 14:45:39', '2018-10-01 14:45:39', NULL),
(61, 'Some Effective Tips for Writing a Successful MBA Application Essay', '<h1>Some Effective Tips for Writing a Successful MBA Application Essay</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Before getting the key points for writing an essay application, it is necessary for the students to understand the need for this application. The student should know this because after knowing the purpose of essay submission with the application will lead to writing an effective essay with their admission application. The university takes admission after determining your communication skills. It determines the clarity, conciseness, fluency and style of portraying your thoughts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The interesting way of your paper is the key element of writing an MBA application essay. It encourages the reader to read your information. Moreover, one of the major elements is the cosiness of your paper that provides ease of reading your information. Following are the more tips that ensure acceptance of the application of the student:</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Open-ended</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The MBA application essay provides no guidance to the students that what should they write and how the paper should organization. However, the student should keep in the mind that this paper demonstrates all the information about the student that is required by the admission community. Moreover, this essay determines the way of communication of the student. This process enables them to demonstrate the skills of the student and it is also observed by the analyst that how this student will be helpful to the community after studying in their university.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Skills</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The MBA application should demonstrate the skills of the student. It should also include the experience and skills of the student as a leader. For the business administration programmes, the leadership skill is a key element. Every student should mention the level of leadership skills present in the personality. It should include the leadership as well as teamwork skills of the student that how the student has worked in the teamwork. Moreover, how it encouraged the team to give the best output to the organization. Hence, the MBA application essay should involve experiences of the student related to the skills and attitudes.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>The growth of the personality</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The student who writes MBA application essay should demonstrate the journey of his life from past to present precisely. It identifies that what the student was in the past and how much he has changed in the present. This may include writing an essay on the professional growth of the student. The student would have to write about a professional career and how he has grown in the past year with his professional career. Furthermore, the application essay for MBA may ask you to write about your growth and how it will be helpful for the growth of a renowned company. &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Planning of the student</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Some of the MBA applications may ask the student to write about the future plan. The student should analyse the current career situation and then think about further objectives of the life in order to link both with each other. The student should also write about short-term and long-term career planning to rectify the position of the career growth. Furthermore, the student should include an intended position and industry for which he wants to work in the future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Precisely, the student should make up his mind from the above key points that how he should prepare his mind for writing the MBA application essay.</p>', 1, 6, 'published', 'some-effective-tips-for-writing-a-successful-mba-application-essay', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 14:55:24', '2018-10-01 14:55:24', NULL),
(62, 'Some Tips to Write an Essay Winningly', '<h1>Some Tips to Write an Essay Winningly</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>An essay is the important part of the university level education. It is beneficial for the students to write their essays effectively. They should gather all the information themselves so that they can increase their knowledge. The essay writing helps the student to develop their skills and develop an understanding of the professional world. Following are some useful tips for students in writing a good an essay and get good grades:</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Selection of the topic</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The effective writing for an essay starts with the selection of the essay. The phenomenon of the essay starts with the selection of the topic. Sometimes the teacher gives any topic to the students to write on the particular topic. When the student sees the topic, they have to analyse the topic from the type of paper that has to produce. The student should narrow the focus.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Prepare an outline for the essay</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>For starting the essay the ideas of the student should be gathered at a point. It is necessary to align the ideas for preparing a document. With the dimension of the thoughts, the student becomes able to structure the essay.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Thesis statement</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>It is one of the important statements in the essay. Every essay is built upon a topic. After sorting out your ideas there is the need to create a thesis statement. The introduction of the essay should include that thesis statement so that the reader can easily understand the theme of the essay.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Work upon body</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The structure of the essay, however, involves introduction, body and conclusion step by step, but the student should write the body first. The body of an essay draws a different opinion, arguments and explanation with respect to the topic. The ideas student gather in the outline should incorporate in each section of the essay. It also creates the separate opinions and arguments. The statement or opinion you have taken from the outline should be written at the start of the paragraph. However, the student should leave three to four lines for an explanation of his opinion and write every opinion in the form of different sections. This practice aligns you with the equality of each section. The student should give an explanation, and support ideas about the opinion. Moreover, examples should be identified form the various sources to support the explanation as well.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Writing an introduction</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>An introduction is the major part of the essay. It should be attractive and develop the interest of your reader. The introduction should necessarily include a thesis statement. Moreover, the student can involve some interesting information, any famous quote or simply summary of the topic. Whatever strategy student uses to grab the reader&rsquo;s attention, it should be clear in the mind that it is relevant to your thesis statement.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Writing conclusion</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The conclusion of the essay should not include new ideas in it. Instead, the student should summarize the entire idea of the essay. It should give the conclusion to your topic. The student should review the main points of the topic and align it with the thesis statement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The student should proofread his topic at the end of the essay so that grammatical errors can be improved and sentences and paragraphs can be linked with each other.</p>', 1, 6, 'published', 'some-tips-to-write-an-essay-winningly', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 15:10:42', '2018-10-01 15:10:42', NULL),
(63, 'Stress-A Significant alarm for Students or Common Health Problem', '<h1>Stress-A Significant alarm for Students or Common Health Problem</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Involvement of students in the mobile phones; using games, social media and different news from the world make them away from the real world in which they live. They are not involved in healthy activities such as playing physical games, attending gatherings &amp; parties and sleeping well. They are getting affected by their physical as well as their mental health due to the unhealthy routine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Today&rsquo;s students want to obtain good grades. They have a competition of grades with their fellows rather than getting knowledge from their studies. This is the reason that less application of the theories has found in the practical life of the students. However, the race of grades among students makes them sleep less and they just want to achieve good grades without understanding the subject. Hence, lack of sleep, the burden of studies and distance from the social life make them isolated and slowly guided towards mental sickness.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is a critical situation for the students that they have to spend their entire life with physical and mental activeness. If they get mentally ill at the end of their graduation, then how will they get ahead with their career and how will they approach towards sustainability in their jobs? The rising stress level of students is destroying the youth. There are several other issues such as traffic, pollution and burden of their personal lives with which students can get stress.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some symptoms of finding someone in stress are:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>A person with the shaking any body part continuously is the major symptom of the stress.</li>\r\n	<li>If you find a person debating ever, it is the major symptom of the stress.</li>\r\n	<li>If you find a person do not pay attention to the daily routine, it is a symptom of stress (it can be a minor kind of stress).</li>\r\n	<li>If you find a person sad most of the time, it seems as he is under stress.</li>\r\n	<li>If you find an enthusiastic person who has changed into accepting failures soon, it is a depressed person.</li>\r\n	<li>If you feel a person who does not make efforts for striving towards his life, it is one of the symptoms of the depression. &nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>If you find a person helpless for the future, it is a minor symptom of stress but it may become major with the passage of time.</li>\r\n	<li>It is one of the major sign of depression that a person remains sitting in the similar position for hours and stares at a particular point for no reason.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Mental illness was considered one of the incurable diseases previously. It was so because there was no predetermination of the stress and depression in the past. People were not aware of the symptoms. Today, we have got remedies for any kind of the diseases. Everyone knows that what he should do to get rid of the disease.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are several doses that can be prescribed by practitioners for reducing stress. However, these doses can make a person addicted that is why one should soon stop using the doses when he starts feeling better.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The role of society is important to remove the stress level of a person:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>If a person is depressed, people should not remind him that he is depressed. They should talk to him about several things, identify the problem of his life and suggest ways to resolve his problem. You should also encourage him to talk more and more so that he can say openly whatever he wants to say.</li>\r\n	<li>If a person is in stress you should encourage him to socialize with people, share his problems with the close one and get time for himself.</li>\r\n	<li>If a person is depressed than you should spend some time with him but do not argue on any of his discussion unless you find betterment in his stress level.</li>\r\n	<li>If a person is in stress, you should take some time for him however, you are not a good friend of him. You should talk him about the things in which he takes interest and gives his opinions.</li>\r\n</ul>', 1, 6, 'published', 'stress-a-significant-alarm-for-students-or-common-health-problem', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 15:25:22', '2018-10-01 15:25:22', NULL),
(64, 'Telling the Importance of Essay Writing', '<h1>Telling the Importance of Essay Writing</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>It is one of the qualities of essay writing is that it can reach a point where professionals reach. It is possible to right in the professional way of writing when you taught the basic skills of writing an essay and when there is need of virtual perfection. People are not educated about the basic principles of writing an essay. The students get essay writing in different courses of their studies. In fact, they have to be aware of essay writing skills before joining the universities because they have to write an essay as part of their applications. The essay writing develops many skills in the students such as:</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Demonstration for understanding material</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether the course belongs to business management, marketing, supply chain, IT, human resource management, sociology, history, psychology or it is any language&rsquo;s grammar, essay teachers give assignments to their students. Students&rsquo; knowledge tests with the tool of the essay. It occurs when students assess their analysis and arguments and specify examples. Then students conclude on the basis of the analysis they conduct. This is an essay that helps students to search for the knowledge and demonstrate their understanding with the help of professional writing skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Development of critical thinking</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Critical thinking refers to a purposeful and reflective analysis that is used to reach conclusions. Essay writing develops critical thinking in a student. Students are asked to gather different arguments from the different sources and align them to identify a conclusion. They are asked to align the texts from the authentic resources. Hence, student gathers knowledge from the different sources such as books, articles, news, magazines and different online resources to gather information with respect to essay topic. It also makes students to analyse the different opinions and get benefit from them. Moreover, students get different relevant and irrelevant information to write his essay.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>The real-life implication</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Essay encourages students to get knowledge of the real life. They read and learn about different topics. It is important to write an essay using information from the authentic resources. It makes students go and learn beyond the academia. Essay enables students to get real-time examples and learn more and more about the professional world.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Structuring assignment</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>An essay requires the appropriate organization of the paper. It is one of the important aspects of writing an essay that teachers develop into students. Whether students complete their assignment by spending a lot of time or write the essay on the day of submission, the arrangement of the paper and placing arguments suitably make teachers grant good marks to the student.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Attracting readers</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The teachers give the essay to develop the skills to write the paper professionally. It makes students understand about the reader first. If the start of the essay is interesting for the reader he would be interested to read the paper. Hence, it is necessary for the students to improve their essays from a readers&rsquo; perspective. It is also recommended to the students to peer review their essays because it improves their grammar and sentence structures.</p>', 1, 6, 'published', 'telling-the-importance-of-essay-writing', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 15:27:50', '2018-10-01 15:27:50', NULL),
(65, 'There Are Two Ways for Writing an Essay Successfully', '<h1>There Are Two Ways for Writing an Essay Successfully</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Essay writing is not an easy task, and it does require to define the structure of the composition first, to create an integrated, coherent and understandable piece. It depends on an essay writer as to select the type of the essay structure, its purpose, and the overall outcome wants to achieve through it. An essay can be argumentative or discursive. However, the selection of the structure depends on the context in which a writer writes an article. Also, it depends on the capability of a writer to select the most feasible or the instructed style to write an article.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As far as the argumentative structure of an essay, a major purpose is to raise an argument and a sequence of counter-arguments against it. It helps to find out a range of diversified ideas, concepts and outcomes. In this way, a reader could develop its opinion, based on the collection of thoughts and ideas. An argumentative essay may be of five types, as debate, persuasive, Rogerian, Toulmin, and satire. A contentious way of the written piece helps to find out all those positive and negative aspects of an issue, topic, or study. For example, it has taken social media as for an argumentative essay, so there could highlight a range of pros and cons of social media, by an essay writer.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>An argumentative essay far more called an investigation carried out by a writer, whereby it needs to collect evidence and present it to the readers. At this stage, it is important to obtain current and valid evidence so that it could grab the attention of the reader, and develop a positive image of the writer. Otherwise, an essay writer must not try to raise fake or invalid arguments that do not have their existence in the real world. It could provide suggestions or recommend actions, based on the predictions or forecasted data.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, a discursive essay collects relevant ideas about the given topic and identified it in the form of an organized structure essay. In a Discursive essay, there is a far more focus on the collection of most relevant ideas, figures, and concepts, rather than raised one argument over the other. Hence, a discursive essay provides an organized structure for the collection of thoughts, relevant ideas and opinions. However, it is important to notice that in a discursive essay, a writer represents the less personal opinion, as compared to the argumentative essay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A discursive essay instead recognized as a formal means of writing, whereby a major purpose is to provide knowledge to a reader, as much as possible. Also, a discursive essay recognized due to the description provided on a given topic. A discursive essay is different from an argumentative essay, due to its persuasive power. An argumentative essay persuades a reader, along with providing education. However, the purpose of a discursive essay is to provide education to the readers, rather less focus on the influential factor. It is, therefore, a discursive essay far consider as a formal means of an essay, due to less or no personal opinion.</p>', 1, 6, 'published', 'there-are-two-ways-for-writing-an-essay-successfully-1', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 15:29:17', '2018-10-01 15:29:17', NULL),
(66, 'Top 5 most effective communication techniques and strategies', '<h1>Top 5 most effective communication techniques and strategies</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Now days focus of organizations have increased in communication to increase productivity as well as quality. They spend more and more money to connect people with each other. For instance, they offer lunches and dinners to their staff so that staff will communicate in the better way. Moreover, organizations also amend their rules and regulations according to the need of the situation of the workplace. The communication, in an organization, requires listening skills, understanding of approach, clarity and conciseness, understanding the situation and analysing feedbacks.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><em>1.Communication and personality difference</em></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>There are different people at a workplace. They may differ from each other in gender, culture, religion etc. They also differ in personality as well. From the Big Five traits, one is the level of extravagance. If a person is extravagant by nature, he would like to be social. He will take interest in the matters of other colleagues. However, if a person is introverted then he would not like socialize with people. He is a reserved person and would not like to share personals with others. In an organization, personality difference is one of the important communication barriers. Organizations should develop an understanding of the personality difference and does not force introvert people to mingle with others. As far as working quality is concerned if everyone does his part efficiently and effectively then it would generate better quality of the operations.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><em>2.Respect others</em></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>An organization is the composition of the people who are senior and working in the organization for many years and junior employees who have joined organization recently. It is the responsibility of an organization, to encourage senior and junior employees so that they can work together. Moreover, senior employees should interact effectively with junior employees in order to share their knowledge. The organization should observe the injustice of every member whether it is an old employee working for many years in the organization or it is the new employee who has recently joined your firm. The organization should not see the one side of the picture and blame only juniors for their behaviour.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><em>3.Clarity and conciseness</em></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Clarity in communication is very important for an organization. It develops with the practice of the employees. As more and more discussion on any topic may produce more ambiguity to the subject, employees should focus on the concerned project and start projecting the work as soon as possible. They should not waste much time in talking here and there. It wastes the resource of time. Sometimes clarity and conciseness produce better results than making long speeches at the workplace. Hence, employees should think and research for the subject matter rather than gossiping.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><em>4.Situational Analysis</em></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>It is the least concerned matter in communication. One has to observe the situation and analyse it carefully in order to develop effective communication. The recipients of communication may differ in skills, grasping power and competencies. It is necessary that recipient and situation contribute in the effective way to propagate with the better input of communication for the best output.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some important observation of the workplace involves:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>There are people in the organization who communicate fast and to the point. They are high achievers because they do not waste their time. However, people with low-level lack this skill and go slow with speech as well as a detailed explanation.</li>\r\n	<li>Business communication requires formal conversation and avoidance of grammar.</li>\r\n	<li>Oral communication has different ways of the pitch for every kind of sentences. Hence, the pitch should be concerned for the betterment in communication.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><em>5.Feedback</em></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Effectiveness in communication does not only require that how sender is communicating, it also focuses that how the receiver is receiving it. For this purpose:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The sender should encourage receiver(s) to ask questions so that misconception can get clear.</li>\r\n	<li>The sender should recognize facial expressions and body language. A blank face expression means the receiver is not getting message properly. Failure of maintaining eye contact represents receivers&rsquo; lack of interest or boredom.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Communication not only benefits a person in the professional life but it also benefits in the personal life. One should adopt an appropriate communication strategy to develop a correct approach of the communication.</p>', 1, 6, 'published', 'top-5-most-effective-communication-techniques-and-strategies', 1, 1, 2, '2018-10-01 15:33:53', '2018-10-01 18:44:51', NULL),
(67, 'How to create an academic paper', '<h1>How to create an academic paper</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Are you curious about academic writing?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This article is best guide for writing academically. It would visualize that how you can create academic paper.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Firstly you should know Academic writing is the process of breaking down ideas and using deductive reasoning, formal voice and it discusses with the third person&rsquo;s voice. It is unlike a blog writing that use first or second person&rsquo;s point of view like I, You, We. Here are some major points of academic writing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are four major types of academic writing:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><em>Descriptive</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>Analytical</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>Persuasive and</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>Critical</em></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>These types are according to the need of preparing a draft.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><em>Descriptive </em></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>You have seen that many assignments require information about a company, its business strategies, its human resources, supply chain, IT infrastructure and finance. It is the simplest form of academic writing but provide comprehensive detail about the company.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><em>Analytical</em></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Analytical approach is different from descriptive one. All academic writing includes appropriate discipline in it. You have to maintain a flow from introduction to conclusion. For example if you prepare analysis in comparison of two countries or two companies, it would involves theories in different form such as social context, practices and language learning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In order to make a paper analytical you have to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Plan, brainstorm facts and ideas and pattern of draft preparation like similarities and differences flow charts, tree diagrams and tables.</li>\r\n	<li>Decide that what are you going to incorporate in this paper</li>\r\n	<li>Built each section on the analytical theme of the particular topic</li>\r\n	<li>Manipulate paper structure</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><em>Persuasive</em></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Persuasive writing is one step ahead of the analytical writing. You can observe the name of persuasive writing that is persuading the facts and figures. Most of the essays include persuasiveness in them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The main theme of persuasive writing basically is evaluation, argument and discussion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For supporting the persuasive facts and ideas you have to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Research other&rsquo;s point of views (particularly scholarly articles and books)</li>\r\n	<li>Look for patterns in data or references to identify strongest evidence</li>\r\n	<li>Identify real-life implications that is beneficial</li>\r\n	<li>Discuss facts and ideas with someone else</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Persuasive kind of papers is also known as<em> argumentative</em> paper, in order to develop argument one has to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Search reasons of what you are writing</li>\r\n	<li>Think and identify different kind of sources as evidence of your point of view</li>\r\n	<li>Develop reasons for what previously written by researchers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Breaking down information and highlight each part such as environmental, cost effectiveness, scope of real-world application and sustainability</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><em>Critical</em></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Critical writing is common among postgraduate, research and advanced undergraduate writing. It involves features of persuasive writing. However, persuasively written papers include at least one point of view and critical analysis involves two viewpoints that is backed by your own opinion at the last.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>An example of this kind of critical academic writing involves a critique from a journal article or literature reviews to identify the strengths and weaknesses of existing research.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are further divisions of critical writing that involves debate, critique, evaluate and disagree.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For establishing a critical academic paper one has to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Provide accurate summary of the discussion</li>\r\n	<li>Your own appropriate opinion for the discussion</li>\r\n	<li>Give evidence of each point of view you incorporated in the paper</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Purpose of academic writing is to develop understanding of the reader. It should be thus, concise and clear.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Most of the college-level research papers involve following elements to be followed:</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong><em>Planned and focused</em></strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The structure of overall assignment should be well prepared, formal and logical. Students may not start with the manipulation of structure from the beginning. But as they go through different sections and questions of their assignments they start preparing a flow of structure.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>Language</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Development of researcher paper involves unambiguity in the assignments. We have to research many things and put all information at one place. For this purpose language may dwindle at several places. In this situation, paragraphs and sentences should be inter-linked with each other. Moreover, vague expressions are avoided in academic writing such as <em>they, people, the organization</em> etc. The assignment should be specific and avoid use of the words such as <em>very, incredible, super</em> etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The important element in academic writing is writing using passive voice. For instance in the following sentence:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tesco use cost-differentiation strategy to remain competent in the market.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tesco and cost-differentiation strategy are important. Hence, you may write it as:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cost-differentiation strategy is focused by Tesco to achieve competency in the industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This practice would enhance different features of writing assignments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>Punctuation</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The academic writing involves concrete, precise and summative narrative tone. Therefore, punctuation marks are required to place at different positions in the paper to make it a formal paper. However, punctuation marks are avoided in the academic writing because it shows over excitement and remains unsophisticated. Dashes and hyphens are minimized in the case of academic writing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>They give an impression of informal writing that is why they are used seldom in the papers. For instance hyphens may use to connect the prefixes like over-burden, multi-dimensional etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>Evidence-Based arguments</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The evidence based arguments give weightage to the authenticity of information provided in your assignment. It is necessary to develop an argument and precisely discuss it. However, there is the need of certain evidence form scholarly articles and books to confirm that these arguments exist in the world previously. This practice is necessary for the document where there is need of proposing solutions for the identified problem (s).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>Complexity and Higher-Order Thinking</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The academic writing involves conciseness and concreteness in it. This is the reason that it requires complexity of the discussion and information provided in the document. Moreover, there should be logical thinking behind information that has received and articulated in the paper. The theme of your paper should be reflective, critical, creative as well as logical.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is also noticeable that paper is relevant to the topic and comprehends knowledge maintaining its relevancy. The ideas should represent in the comprehensive manner advocating explanation about the opinion you have articulated.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This understanding of kind of academic writing and tips articulated will help students to develop clear explanation towards reader that what you want to state. Precisely, it will portray your opinion.</p>', 1, 7, 'published', 'how-to-create-an-academic-paper', 1, 1, 3, '2018-10-01 15:53:53', '2018-10-01 16:02:17', NULL),
(68, 'Lesson from My Internship', '<h1>Lesson from My Internship</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>An internship is a great idea and opportunity to start a career. It is the new challenge and the best way for every student to find out better job as possible. This blog has been hardest to write for me. In this part, I am trying to sum up the overall lesson that I have learned from my internship program.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>My internship experience has taught me a lot. I have never imagined such things that I could learn. I was an intern at Social Media Marketing. I feel that my duties were ever-changing and diverse. Sometimes it is very tough for me to recall everything that I have performed so many tasks over the past months.&nbsp; But I feel that I have learned most of the beneficial lesson. I am going to describe my overall lesson from my internship experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>What I have learned from my internship</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><u><strong>How to behave in the office</strong>:</u> This is the first step in my learning experience. It is my first position in an office decorum. I did not know exactly what to expect. The environment of the office is quietly relaxed and peaceful. It taught me how to behave at the workplace. Working in the office and getting used to about everything has prepared me about my position in the office. I have observed that everyday event has taught me how to react and handle any situation at the workplace. How to work with a team and how to manage all the official activities. The reality is, the atmosphere thought me a lot about everything, how staff come together and do the right things.&nbsp; Even though sometimes I have to remind myself to use my inside voice and perception. Overall I feel that I have adapted the official life very well.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><u><strong>Build your career-level by connecting people</strong>:</u> I always hear that how it is important to know about the industry and leaders. But it is also an essential part to make practices to be loyal with horizontal management and build the relationship with peoples who are at your same career level. It is not important that which industry you are in. So, I make connections with my managers and team leaders and coordinators who guided me a lot in my overall internship tenure. I noted all their skills and expertise that will help in my career level. I followed their instructions and gave the appropriate output of the work. They appreciated me for my work. It is very beneficial to boost my motivation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><u><strong>To keep writing</strong>:</u> This is very huge for me. I always enjoyed writing and I have the pretty experience to write blogs and articles. So, this position taught me that I need to improve more writing skills. I did not have must skills that I had thought. Writing requires a lot of practice, and I was not practicing enough. Writing for web content, social media and research papers could be more different. In this internship, I have learned that I have to adopt new writing skills with the unique tone. I have to add some value to my writing. This position taught me that every day I have to write something new, I this way I have got a drastic improvement in my writing skills.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><u><strong>Target searching and accomplishing</strong>:</u><strong> </strong>It is the core part of any company to achieve its goals and target. In fact, it also pertains to every employee and intern to attain its target. It might be daily, weekly or monthly. In my internship program, I read many publications and articles related to social media marketing and web content. I also follow those writers who are admired by the public. I had more focus on my daily targets. I wrote a new thing with new improvements. I try to accomplish my daily target with appropriate feedback from my seniors. I read social media platform to get the better feel about the office culture. Moreover, I engaged with social media. And I have got too much interest in the company&rsquo;s events.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><u><strong>Punctuality in all aspects</strong>:</u> Punctuality is the essence of every success. It is followed by every company or office, either small or big company. On the first day of my internship at the office, I saw every employee was punctual. I also have learned how punctuality leads the success and manage time help to get right things done. It shows the dedication and dignity of your work. I delivered my punctual role at my office. It taught me professionalism, capabilities and responsibility.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><u><strong>Diverse culture</strong>:</u> Culture is one of the favorite things in my internship program. I felt that I was lucky to work with a diverse culture. They had bounced ideas continuously with extremely innovative. I taught that in my internship program there were so many new growth opportunities in writing for both as a person and as a professional. I thought it is the best part of the company, that every employee had a passion for start-up and drove change for future technologies and media.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><u><strong>Enhance project management skills</strong>:</u> In my internship program, I worked with web content and media marketing team. I designed media marketing flowchart and diagrams in my project. It helps to improve the overall experience of the employee. I applied my professional writing skills in project designing and planning for both team projects internal and external. These project plans allowed me to demonstrate my abilities to think about strategic management such as &ldquo;outside the box&rdquo;. It helped to deliver the innovative solutions to the team. I also worked with outside consultants in my internship programs on various web and media marketing projects. I taught a lot to transform my writing skills on several writing platforms.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Now, in the end, I want to thank my seniors who helped me in my internship program. They taught me a lot. I have learned a great lesson from my internship experience. And I will be forever indebted to those who gave me a huge hand here. Lastly, I would like to recommend to all those people who are going to start their internship goals, always remember to be friendly with others, work hard and ask questions. I am hoping that everyone will focus and come up with the internship as much as I did.</p>', 1, 7, 'published', 'lesson-from-my-internship', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 15:57:42', '2018-10-01 15:57:42', NULL);
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `title`, `body`, `user_id`, `category_id`, `status`, `slug`, `tag_id`, `confirmed`, `views`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `deleted_at`) VALUES
(69, 'Digital Era and Homeschooling – Effectiveness and Concerns', '<h1>Digital Era and Homeschooling &ndash; Effectiveness and Concerns</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The homeschooling is undoubtedly offering the opportunities for the children and students suffering from learning disabilities and falling through cracks in traditional public schools. It is something that is considered as an outlet for overachievers who feel themselves as limited by the age and grade level. In this age of technology, the homeschooling has broken down the demographics of the average home-school family and found that the parental education of the students is lining up as the identical to all other students. Additionally, the digital technology has made the homeschooling more realistic in today&#39;s world. It allows the parents to tap into the online resources while reaching the subject they are unsure of it. Students are merely reaching out to the digital tutors in order to get help wherever they are stuck. In fact, different creators are providing educational materials for homeschoolers who are going to do most supervising and teaching. In the last few years, the service providers have designed new materials with having parents in their mind. Therefore, it was easy to be followed and to understand what the kids are learning. According to the experts, the online schools are well educating the students for their future. The virtual school are available all over the world that is helpful in integrating the students. It helps in providing meaning to the students in learning their work online but goes to the classroom to test their projects. The students can get some digital options there. Homeschooling is helpful for students to learn the same content as traditional students. Some students learn faster and are not bogged down by waiting for their classmates in order to catch them while other students can take their time on some trickier subjects.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Homeschooling is useful in this digital era as it exceeds with other options for the education in many different reasons. The statistical data proves that the homeschoolers are continuously achieving higher test scores than the students attending public and private schools. It has seen that the homeschooled students are getting the much better education from those who are attending public schools. The homeschoolers are learning better socialization skills that are away from the danger of peer pressure and associated with public and private schools. The homeschooling is useful for the parents in order to get the opportunity to know where their children are academically, socially, and morally. The parents are not worried about their children in homeschooling, and their children are not getting negative influences from other children. The homeschooling is helpful in learning the study skills and developing the ability to direct and organize them towards the goal. The children who are getting homeschooling are learning and becoming more dedicated and responsible for their schoolwork. The parents like tablets use some of the digital tools, a mobile application for education that is helpful to get educated their children and provide them vast knowledge with the digital technologies. The digital technology is considered one of the essential parts of the child&#39;s world. The child uses it to connect with each other, learn new skills, and pursue it with interests. Digital technology in homeschooling is helpful in offering new opportunities for teachers and leaders. It provides new ways for living in the community and child&#39;s learning. The homeschooling is useful for the parents who have decided to embrace the technology. The families in homeschooling are embracing the advance in technologies that are helpful to allow in teaching the children more effectively. It is useful in explaining the children by using technologies, and it introduces other variables into classroom management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The homeschooling concerns with the digital era and technology by shifting in the use of technology by the parents and contrast to formal school settings. The parents in homeschooling are playing a vital role by using advanced techniques and aids for the learning process. It tends to shy away from the use of technology in the classroom. It supports the claim and separates the use of technology in order to access it. The technology is seldom used to assist in the teaching. It is reflecting the widening gap in technology use and attitudes about the usefulness of enhancing student learning. The parents are also taking advantages of the wide variety of education technology available for teaching different subjects that are nor familiar. The homeschooling websites are also available for the parents that help them to learn more about the knowledge and information to educate their children. The sites are available for different subjects, and some books are available as supplement curriculum. It ensures the child through an understanding of the issues that feel comfortable in teaching. The role of the parents in homeschooling and learning tasks are contrasted with different formal school parent. The official school parents are also not involved with direct instruction as homeschooled parents. They spend a significant amount for instructional time with their children in the form of homework. The parents are expecting to help their children in doing their homework. Moreover, the parents are encouraged assisting the child&#39;s homework based on the findings that need parent&#39;s involvements and influence the students&#39; success. The studies found that the situation in the school parents and spending time in teaching their children are through the medium of homework. Thus, the parents are forming the school settings in less involving the academic lives of their children and accomplishing them through expected homework mentoring. The technology has become the useful tool that for homeschooling and allows the parents to achieve the educational outcomes that are similar to those of children in the formal school setting. It is increasing the use of technology in the classroom and the help to support the teacher-student styles. It is important to provide education in the 21st century to improve teaching and learning styles from the available technological tools. The technology used by the parents in giving homeschooling to their children is the best opinion and belief for the role of technology in the learning process.</p>', 1, 7, 'published', 'digital-era-and-homeschooling-effectiveness-and-concerns', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 16:00:10', '2018-10-01 16:00:10', NULL),
(70, 'Establishing A Sustainable Online Identity', '<h1>Establishing A Sustainable Online Identity</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The establishing a sustainable online identity has become a hot topic due to intense proliferation of social media and websites in dynamic business atmosphere. The online identity facilitates the transaction in present digital world and also improves the user&rsquo;s functionality. The online identity intended to permit the recognition of any online entity by means of any electronic channels. According to world economic forum, the online identity of any business is considered as the unique and single most assets. Conversely, a shocking information amount over the web ensures the critical management of presence. The few instances of online identities are shown in following chart.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://medium.localhost/wysiwyg/5084abc.png\" style=\"height:389px; width:1078px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Business website must consider three main areas that are offering information about customers, providing the capability of e-commerce and encouragement of building interactive association among organization and their customers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let&rsquo;s say, to improve the sustainability of online identity, it is essential to contribute actively for individual profile sites. The deed of registration of website will established a positive case of reputation. The occasional visibility and engagement in certain activities of industry and forum discussion will provide the positive content for offsetting the negative feedback in random way that all passionate entrepreneurs is ensure to develop.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Blogging is considered as the ideal manner for expression of positive norms, displaying your expertise along with establishment of company as the influencer. If it is effectively done, it would provide the wealth of positive feedbacks. In addition, it will also serve as the real juice of Google for pushing negative out from the results of any search engine. The business work actively to remove unwanted and irrelevant content.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here is also some proprietary tool on different expert sites for instance <strong><em>&ldquo;Brand Yourself&rdquo; </em></strong>for removing the negative and depraved content. It can be helpful for maintaining a positive online reputation. Don&rsquo;t ignore the negative reviews and ensue the negative monitoring of web to address the negative comment in direct manner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://medium.localhost/wysiwyg/2166cdb.png\" style=\"height:549px; width:975px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>I believe that content in any form such as blog, video, books; podcast and other should be valuable and consistent.&nbsp; The offering value by means of online community across entire channels of social media is integral for sustainable online growth of business.&nbsp; I would also recommend the Pareto Principle of 80/20 rule; share the content of other people or business 80% and personal content with 20% in time instant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hence what&rsquo;s the preeminent tactic for drawing individual in your business world? - The answer is to find the online individual group, avatar or community that contains that person that are sharing the similar interest and running identities or niche business. Then gradually start relationship building by offering value and become the active group member.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The specific metrics of digital identity has become the outstanding predictors for growth of revenue and brand share price in extensive categories array. With the passage of time, a real time and cognitive intelligence of digital identity can identify that legitimate based of customers relied on myriad continuing shifting variables. Yet, another paramount significance should be given to cyber-attacks that can be highly devastating for the prosperity and success of business.</p>', 1, 7, 'published', 'establishing-a-sustainable-online-identity-1', 1, 1, 2, '2018-10-01 16:07:12', '2018-10-01 16:07:34', NULL),
(71, 'Following the Rules of English Grammar for Essay Writing', '<h1>Following the Rules of English Grammar for Essay Writing</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Academic writing usually follows formal writing. The rules of grammar are followed effectively in it. The document remains precise, consistent and coherent. In many academic writing documents common mistakes of English Grammar have seen. These are the grammatical errors that have seen repeatedly. They get appear repeatedly in different academic and non-academic papers. With the Grammar errors the work get dull or weak and writers would never like that there effort goes dull or weak.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are some rules of English grammar that should be followed to write an effective paper:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>Tenses:</em></strong> You should use appropriate noun, verb and adjectives used in your tense. &nbsp;Appropriate positioning of noun, verb and adjective intensify the knowledge that you want to articulate in your text. Moreover, there are different types of tenses beyond present, past and future tenses that are needed to place accurately.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>Punctuation</em></strong>: Capital letter should be used appropriately at the start of sentence and for proper noun. A major mistake done at the end of question is dual punctuation signs. You should avoid this mistake and appropriately put the question mark on it. Moreover, placing apostrophe is also required to place to show the ownership. Commas also get misused during sentences. You have to manage use of commas and strike very it is appropriate and you find its need.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>Homophones:</em></strong> Homophones put the sentence in doubt. They create confusion towards reader. Unfortunately, spell checker cannot track it. Sometimes it supports to catch the words such as &ldquo;there&rdquo; or &ldquo;their&rdquo;. But most of the time it is not able to detect the words such as &ldquo;were&rdquo; or &ldquo;wear&rdquo;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>Adjectives and adverbs</em></strong>: There are some adjectives to define the state or characteristic. However, adverbs are used to advance or modify those of the adjectives. &nbsp;In this sentence &ldquo;The fox jumped quick&rdquo; there is wrong use of adjective because &ldquo;The fox jumped quickly&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>Abbreviations and acronyms</em></strong>: People now days create acronyms themselves that are not recognizable specifically in an academic writing. Hence, firstly, writer has to check that acronym he is using is correct or not if he finds reluctance in using it. Acronym should be well-known among your targeted audience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>Subject and verb</em></strong>: You should use sentences that have appropriate match of the subject with the verb. For the initiators of English language or people who speak English as the second language cannot understand the mismatch of subject with verb. Such as sentence <em>she have two cats</em> is not a right sentence, it should be <em>she has two cats</em> or <em>she possesses two cats</em>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Use of &ldquo;ve&rdquo;: Some people use should&rsquo;ve and could&rsquo;ve in the sense of &ldquo;of&rdquo;. However, meaning of &ldquo;ve&rdquo; is have. Hence, they should take care of using abbreviations and contractions. The sentence structure gets change with this mistake of using &ldquo;ve&rdquo; in place of &ldquo;of&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Students can get effective English Grammar rules using above knowledge of common mistakes. However, the key element in structuring sentences is flow of the sentences and their coordination with each other.</p>', 1, 7, 'published', 'following-the-rules-of-english-grammar-for-essay-writing-1', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 16:10:31', '2018-10-01 16:10:31', NULL),
(72, 'How can students overcome the issue when ideas/mind is blocked?', '<h1>How can students overcome the issue when ideas/mind is blocked?</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>When you continuously reading or attempting any assignment, you get stuck with your mind and it becomes uneasy to keep working ahead. It happens to a lot of people, including me. Many of the students also get blocked with the idea to take initiative even. Here we talk about mind restriction during our work and I will share different ways of taking you out from the situation in this article:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Change, re-arrange or clean your environment</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are continue to work in the similar environment and finding yourself obsessed with the non-creation of the ideas then you should change your mind by engaging yourself in surrounding. For sure, you will find a messy bedroom around you. You may at least arrange your workplace to divert your attention.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>However, if you are an organized person, you have better option to go to your kitchen and have water, juice, or anything you want to drink or eat.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Prepare a Board to write your goals</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You need a board, sketchbook or journal near you when you study. At the point when you stuck with brainstorming and different ideas, you need to write or sketch your achievements till the time. You may analyse while writing that how much work you have done and how much is left. Hence, you can also create some target to achieve from now.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Understanding nature</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nature attracts people and de-stressed them. Not necessarily, nature is going towards ocean, parks and greenery. If you not find this kind of area, you have an open sky to walk beneath it. You can leave working for some minutes and get back to the nature to relax your mind for a while.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Get away from technology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is said that technology has fasten our world. It is digital age and relaxation is different in this era. However, research has evident that our brain need get rid for sometimes from the modern technology. It is not so that using Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, listening music and watching TV make you away from technology. &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These technologies in fact, raise the level stress among users. It is also evident from research that creativity blocks technology. In this situation, downtime is necessary to remove constraints of the brain.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Listen to music</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Music has found to affect the process of learning and thinking. It is the good source of developing motivation to the work. You can take some break and start listening music for some minutes to get your mind back to the task. You should know doctors emphasize that flat notes of music encourage sleep and natural notes give alertness, otherwise you may get more blocked with your brain when you listen the plain music.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Create deadline</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is necessary to establish a deadline for the accomplishment of your task or accomplishing it to the particular time. It will provide you ease of formation of the small goals of your task. You would like to do your work quickly and where you will find difficulty only that time will hinder your accomplishment of the small goals of your task.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This article has given you guidance when you get blocked with your brain. Hence, you can select any one of them to re-furnish your activity.&nbsp;</p>', 1, 7, 'published', 'how-can-students-overcome-the-issue-when-ideasmind-is-blocked', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 16:18:16', '2018-10-01 16:18:16', NULL),
(73, 'How to approach an essay on Management?', '<h1>How to approach an essay on Management?</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Writing an essay is one of the essential parts in academic program. Management is a field of study that possess variations in it. Academic success of the student can be boost with the help of well-written and informative essay while you may get an end to the dreams if paper is poorly written. The essay is written to identify the knowledge of theories related to the field of subject. Following are some key areas on which student can focus to write a better essay:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Identification of instructions and requirements</li>\r\n	<li>Prepare a draft</li>\r\n	<li>Abide the rules while preparing the document</li>\r\n	<li>Manipulate your essay</li>\r\n	<li>Clarity maintenance</li>\r\n	<li>Elude grammatical mistakes</li>\r\n	<li>Finishes with relevancy to the topic</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The essay writing mainly involves three major areas:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Introduction</li>\r\n	<li>Body and</li>\r\n	<li>Conclusion</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>Introduction</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>You have to start with the introduction of the topic and give brief description about what you are going to discuss in entire essay. This is the introductory paragraph of your essay. It is necessary in academic writing that it involves precise details of what you are going to discuss ahead. It should be attractive paragraph that grab attention of the reader to read entire essay with the interest. It is thus, essential to mention a thesis statement at the end of the introduction. Thesis statement is sentence that summarizes the entire essay into one sentence. It is necessary to put in introductory part of the essay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em>Discussion/body</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For establishing your argument you have to select two or more arguments for your statement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You have to select argument and discuss it in the supportive or argumentative manner. It has to maintain theme of the thesis statement in order to maintain relevancy to the topic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After discussing thesis statement you should now examine, search and identify the argument that support or oppose your thesis statement (the evidence are provided in the form of references at the end of the draft). It discusses different point of views from the different scholars. It may involve discussion form the books or real-time examples.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Then it comes to conclude your essay. Concluding an essay is the critical part of the document. It involves all the key points of the discussion took place in the body or discussion part of the essay. It follows the implication of the discussion in the real-time. Moreover, it presents each view of the discussion in precise manner. Then writer has to put his opinion that is based on the discussion presented in overall paper.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It has to manage the theme of discussion to incorporate the findings of the discussion and relate both to create comprehensive research on the essay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Students have to focus on academic writing criteria to prepare a good document that may include:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Precision of sentences</li>\r\n	<li>Maintaining language and its elements</li>\r\n	<li>Punctuation</li>\r\n	<li>Comprehensive of discussion</li>\r\n	<li>Development of arguments</li>\r\n	<li>Appropriate referencing</li>\r\n	<li>Following international formats of writing academic paper</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>With the clear understanding of above point, an student can good marks in academic journey.</p>', 1, 7, 'published', 'how-to-approach-an-essay-on-management-1', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 16:20:06', '2018-10-01 16:20:06', NULL),
(74, 'How to Create an Essay Outline?', '<h1>How to Create an Essay Outline?</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Everything requires proper planning and organizing. Similarly, academic writing also needs to develop structure or format of an essay or a report that you are going to prepare. It should be prepared keeping all the instructions in mind. Moreover, student is required to collect information of the material that he wants to include in the essay. An essay involves three major parts that are <strong><em>introduction, body and conclusion</em></strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>An outline should involve all the headings and subheadings that you are going to incorporate in your essay. For example if you are going to prepare an essay on advantages and disadvantages of social media then it would not only articulate advantages and disadvantages of the social media. You would have to give introduction of your document before starting advantages and disadvantages of it. Then you would have to state its history and then you come towards advantages and disadvantages.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>An example of outlining essay is:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.Introduction</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1.1 History of Social media</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.Evolution of internet</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2.1 Development of social networks</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Advantages of social media</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3.1 Education Field</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3.2 Business field</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3.3 Consumers</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Disadvantages of social media</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4.1 Crime</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4.2 Online sexual exploitation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4.3 Cyber bullying</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4.4 Addiction to social media</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5.Conclusion</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6.Recommendation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is the appropriate outline of an essay. It depicts that one should begin with structuring <strong><em>introduction</em></strong> of the topic. Your introduction should define that what is your topic about and what its significance is in the current era. It should necessarily articulate a thesis statement at the end of the introduction. Your thesis statement will be your topic of discussion that you will lead ahead. Hence, its highlighted appearance is necessary in your introduction.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Then it is not necessary that you come to the topic directly. It will give comprehensiveness to your paper if you will describe the <strong><em>history </em></strong>of the organization, channels, person or any other thing in detail. When you put different material for the relevant topic in your paper, it identifies that you have planned and organized your paper by giving it appropriate time. It was not just you sit, searched for the topic directly, write about it with the lack of interest in the topic.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Then you can come towards the topic as shown in the example &ldquo;Advantages of Social Media&rdquo;. It is not like you have searched for the advantages and disadvantages and documented in the form of plain text. There can be creation of some subheadings as you begin with writing and find suitable headings for the kind of advantage. Similarly, you may create subheadings for the &ldquo;Disadvantages of Social Media&rdquo; as well.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After comprehensive discussion of advantages and disadvantages of social media, you should <strong><em>conclude</em></strong> your discussion you have made previously. Firstly, you have needed to articulate the summary or key points of both advantages and disadvantages of the social media. Then you would have to come towards your opinion about topic. You would have to give your opinion regarding your entire essay in one point. If it is required you have to <strong><em>recommend</em></strong> kind of beneficiaries or affected people about using or not using the social media.</p>', 1, 7, 'published', 'how-to-create-an-essay-outline-1', 1, 1, 2, '2018-10-01 16:26:00', '2018-10-01 16:44:14', NULL),
(75, 'How to Finance Your Travel While Studying?', '<h1><strong>How to Finance Your Travel While Studying? </strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The international Higher education has become an excellent manner for enhancing the overall academic experience. It resulted in the improved awareness of culture as well as tolerance. The abroad education is helpful for the development of in-depth realization of the world and has the vital contribution in marketability of career specifically personal growth. The contemporary organizations are seeking for human resources having excellent skills of communication as well as cross culture capabilities that can be foster by overseas education. The studying in the foreign country is the highly expensive process. There is some manner for helping the international education for the purpose of funding. The three most prevailing potential sources for abroad funding are Scholarships, Financial Aid as well as Loans.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Scholarship:</strong> A scholarship is considered as the excellent sources that neglected by the majority of students due to a complicated procedure. A student can be highly overwhelmed at the time of application and absolute time is required for scouring the scholarship. A standardized search on the web would lead to ample outcomes and communication with overseas education advisor is considered as the critical element. The conversation with an advisor assures enabling the required information from an authentic and reliable source. The international education advisor can refer the small scholarship not offering adequate money, however, are not as much as competitive, and also elevated the shot to earn the additional stream of money. In a few instances, Universities offered the scholarship to those students that are capable of writing a substantial essay on the subject of how abroad studying is significant and what is anticipated to attain from the abroad semester.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Financial Aid:</strong> A careful and vigilant approach must be taken to avail financial aid. As all universities might have different policies. The abroad semester has become highly famous among students, and there are so many schools that are offering the financial aid package for overseas education. It indicates that the deal considered for financial aid office is remaining pertinent for obtaining the experience of abroad study. If your school or colleges don&rsquo;t have the adequate policy, then the best approach is based on the adoption of a proactive approach from a financial aid office. Inquire them about anything for application in specific available aid packages. It may or may not end up luckily.&nbsp; The sole manner to ensure about this fact is to ask with financial power for earning the additional source of money.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Loans:</strong> The loans are considered as the most viable option. Nevertheless, the consideration of a loan requires a cautious approach. Recall that there is disparity among loan, scholarship and financial aid that students have to pay back for each dollar for students after the graduation of students. Certainly, it must be the double check to determine if there is any Perkin or Stafford alternative; however, it is highly lean. By relying on the credit or else co-signer credit, a student can look for the private loan from banks. However, the loan from bank evolved with the unfortunate slap of greater rate of interest; however, a majority of students can be turned into private sources of a loan when money is required and recognized that fact that it evolved with the additional cost. Extensive research is required for the selection of right bank that can be shaved off with the greater rate of interest. However, a rationale warning is that rates are identical across different institutions due to existing economy state and federal reserves to establish the standards of borrowing.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Students should not be afraid of seeking multiple sources of funds such as the combination of loan and scholarship. It is considered as the financial idea, and well-advised opine and adoption of a proactive planning approach will make the overall process simple and easier.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Don&rsquo;t forget to consider the traditional and conventional options for saving. As student decided for overseas studying, the student can work to save for the trips. It is advised to adopt a realistic approach as saving merely is not adequate for sufficient funding. Nonetheless, saving is considered as the most obvious manner for affording the abroad education. Every little bit saving is helpful for spending less on unessential binges. Prior to making a huge buying; ask them, if a purchase is more important than overseas education. If you sacrifice the purchase for the sake of studying abroad, each penny or dollar saving reduces the proximity for fulfilling the financial requirement of study abroad.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Another alternative to arranging the financial funds is to seek relative help. The overseas education is the highly expensive process; however, it is considered as the future investment. The parent and near relative can be willing to help and arrange the financial funds. The student can also establish a fund for travelling to save the money for studying abroad. One can write blogs to seek financial help and added the donation button on some Master Cards, to make it simple for any individual to gain some money to avail financial assistance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The students can also apply for the aid through the school or give an application for federal aid from the reference of school or college. Moreover, many international educational institutes are offering financial aid to a few overseas students on the basis of merit, in spite of financial backgrounds. The type of aid varied from different universities and educational study level. More assistance is offered for graduate education and rather fewer for undergraduate educational programs. The financial funds are perceptively available in different fields such as physical, engineering and biological science in spite of management, social science and humanities. For seeking the financial aid, it is required to submit the form to apply for the financial aid that will be offered to school/college and scholarship service board is responsible for administering the overall procedure.</p>', 1, 7, 'published', 'how-to-finance-your-travel-while-studying', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 16:28:38', '2018-10-01 16:28:38', NULL),
(76, 'How to Hire A Remote Worker', '<h1>How to Hire A Remote Worker</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Here, the Remote work brings a paradigm shift and revolutionise the working way.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Let&rsquo;s Say: It is loud and pleasant for the people at back:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The progression and technological challenges have been mitigated the challenges being remote employees.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Remote working requires diverse indulgent for communication and collaboration, certainly. However, eventually it should not be considered as the work experience of inferior quality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The evolving trend of Remote Working has constructed the landscape of labour. The organisations are progressively adopted the approach of remote hiring for their business, enabling their staff to work from their convenience i.e. from home. On the contrary, the strategizing manner to work from home, landing mobile gigs and remain focussed in office work. The Remote workers, like other employees, required open communication with clear expectation set.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://medium.localhost/wysiwyg/3132remote.jpg\" style=\"height:720px; width:1280px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A viable strategy for hiring remote work is expansion of network on larger scale. For the opening of any remote job, there are different channels specifically reaching the network, including friends &amp; family, referrals, business partners and others. The Employee Referral is considered as the preeminent quality source for new recruiters. The onsite job is concentrated on geographical area, however for remote workers; it is required to broaden your horizon and thinking approach. The perspective employees can be expanded unto candidate all over the globe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The job evaluation process for the remote job will commence from the early communication and paying high attention to different behaviours when conduct interview with remote candidate.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>How fastly they act in response against email and calls?</li>\r\n	<li>Are they effectively able to communicate over the phone call as well as in writing?</li>\r\n	<li>Are they excellent verbal communicator?</li>\r\n	<li>What are their technological expertise for establishing and running a home office?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I believed that ideal remote candidate must have the ingenuity and creativity for resolution of challenges on self-behalf and required marginal or no peripheral support and assistance.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>An integral element of hiring strategy is based on effective value proposition of employee and mainly includes culture, mission, compensation, benefits and generally the element of bigger strategy of employer branding. For appealing the remote employees, the employee value proposition required additional emphasis on flexibility and assist the remote workforce to feel as the important part of team. An example of employee value proposition is software for email marketing and help desk for remote working employees.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The majority of remote position can be recruited by phone interview or might involve video interview that is more identical with individual interview-Few of the recruitment procedure can be refined further for supporting the goals of remote employees. During the recruitment procedure, a smart approach is based on skills and approach of candidate by conducting a trial project or small test, to observe, how effectively or not, the remote employees are following the instruction, asking questions, and in general actively performing in remote ambiance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>The real secret lies in the fact that excellent remote management involves best off site practices. It is not so challenging, rather it offer challenges to managers for working harder and doing better. The remote employees are more productive in spite of forcing arbitrarily to work in set fixed hours.</em></p>', 1, 7, 'published', 'how-to-hire-a-remote-worker-1', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 17:35:12', '2018-10-01 17:35:12', NULL),
(77, 'How to Plan Education and Avoid Exams Stress', '<h1>How to Plan Education and Avoid Exams Stress</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Stress is considered ad the pessimism product. The thinking for the negative thing side enables the student to subject towards more towards studies. The adoption of a positive approach can mitigate the exam stress. The student can encourage themselves by being a student, and it becomes easier to get a good score in the examination. The majority of students can confront the anxiety of exam, would include additional worry about the future study, fear of evaluation, consequences apprehension, and managed to follow a plan for practical recommendations. The factors contributing anxiety are based on poor nutrition, inadequate exercise, various stimulants, and problems of time management. The everyday stress relieving tips are self-beliefs, no excessive worrying, not tried to become perfect, take action for minimizing the issues and others. The adoption of a positive mantra is helpful for keeping the mood happy during studies. When feeling stressed, the positive mantra can be repeated by adopting in-depth and sooth breaths. The mediation for relaxation is the best way for the avoidance of worrying regarding the performance in the examination. The students can also try Yoga for self-relaxation. During the exams, the use of social media must be avoided as the majority of class fellows and friends are more prone for conversing about their studies related apprehension. It is recommended to never think about failure during examination as it can lead to deprived performance and it is advised to deal with stress level tactfully. The exam tension should not overcome the preparation during exams.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Every student plans its education to get some goal and achieve performance in academic records. In this way, the student receives a lot of stress. It is an unavoidable part of every student&#39;s life. It could lead to fierce competition. But stress exists due to some reasons, and many of the students try to overcome the stress level to improve their work. The educational plan helps to reduce your stress and make you in an organised way. You need to learn more about effective planning for your education. You must be more focused in order to get prepare for your exams. Most of the students make their study plan, which is not the big issue for students. They took some initiatives and became more motivated and productive. Every day they use different approaches to study and make a clear understanding of the active learning process. The students use different learning platforms and tools the help them to align their goals for day-to-day study. The combat exam stress that allows every student to understand the difficulty and anxiety during studying or making education plans. This combat stress method helps to reduce the pressure of exams. The student should ask for help from other classmates if he or she found an issue in the learning process. Combined group study is also useful to avoid stress during exams. The student can also ask the teacher and discuss the best ways of learning during exams. The teachers have many years of the learning experience, and they can share with you. Teachers also provide feedback for improvement in reviews.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even the most intense schedule of the exams does not allow the time for a study break. It may include the crack of 20 minutes during the revision and no longer are activities looking forward to doing it. It may be helpful to go to the cinemas with friends and do more things in the spare time that takes the mind off from exams&#39; stress. The spending of a little time with books is helpful in making the student relax for the next time he comes to revise. If the pressure gets on, therefore; it is better to talk to someone and seek help in sharing the points. Try to speak about the issues related to education and concerns and ask for the advice on how to manage it. It is something a big step for the family member about the pressure a student feels. In order to reduce stress, it is essential to organize the work and learn more about planning and looking after the person. It is also helpful in focusing on the preparations for the exams. It is useful for the students to go out for a walk or run towards the pleasant weather in order to reduce the exam stress. It helps in keeping them healthy and boosts the mood in making it more productive while revising. It is better to provide proper breathing techniques that make the person more relaxed, help them from medications in calming down, and beat the stress.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The exams stress could better reduce by setting out appropriate goals to manage the coursework as well as lectures, covered up in the module. It needs decide the timeframe to cover up each subject and its different disciplinary subjects. Along with this, it needs to set out proper activities to study, such as study online, physically, or combine study will carry out, to promote the learning experience. Otherwise, without setting out the goals, all the entire learning phase will be haphazard, and there may be several important points, missed by a student. Not only had this, but exams stress impact on an individual, physically as well as mentally.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It could also apply several physical activities, such as a good and healthy diet, proper sleep, and setting out a timeframe for study, could provide far better results to a student. It impacts on the physical health of an individual so that they could not feel exaggerated, or hydrated, due to the deficiency of food. Also, the deficiency of proper diet caused distracts the mindset, and an individual could not concentrate on its work or study. For this reason, specifically during exams, it is important to take a healthy and proper diet. Further, students could also take part in the anti-exam stress program, whereby a student learn several different exercises, as well as healing techniques, to relax and concentrate on their study, without imposing it as stress. Also, exam stress could better overcome during exams via arriving at the exam centre, early.</p>', 1, 8, 'published', 'how-to-plan-education-and-avoid-exams-stress', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 18:36:26', '2018-10-01 18:36:26', NULL),
(78, 'How to Plan your Travel While in Study?', '<h1>How to Plan your Travel While in Study?</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>I will provide some tips to plan the ultimate trips on the weekend.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The favourite part of a majority of overseas students is based on travelling while in Study. The international students loved to plan to prolong excursion based on multi-countries. The majority of travelling is done during the weekend when there are not test and assignment to make. The planning of hassle-free travel on the weekend will result in higher gratification level of students.&nbsp; In the UK the semester ends in mid of June and recommence from September, it is like about 12 Weeks. In six months, students can earn money wherein the remaining six months; the students can do something exciting and refreshing such as travelling.&nbsp; The best thing is hanging out with international students as it is helpful for learning about the globe, ensure the vicariously travelling across the specific parts of the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are some cheap flights available in the UK that makes the life highly exciting if overseas students flash their student&rsquo;s cards. The overseas students in the UK can plan for the second trip to Europe as it free or require minimal expenses to see a lot of things specifically on behalf of student card. The travelling in holiday time will provide the lifelong and high-grade learning lesion and also boost up the productivity as well as skills for the organisation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I believed that spending holidays with friends brings more fun and slightly safer as compared to travel alone. The multiple heads can work together to make the planning more straightforward and easier. Hence, it&rsquo;s better to accompanied by friends. It is advised to plan a budget for flight as well as hostel before travel. The flying on low-cost carriers such as Ryanair and Easy Jet are considered as the cost-effective option. Even though these airline carriers are not cost-effective, however for the group of students, it doesn&rsquo;t matter in a lot and can be a fun loving experience for the students.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is recommended to stay in hostels that are pretty much cost effective and conduct web research on the city prior to travel to the town. The primary city research involves the remarkable use of maps, guidance for language, and advice for health. I firmly believe that the more knowledge you have about the culture and historical background of the place, this instance resulted in more appreciation about the trip. Most important advice is to bring the copy of the passport and visa for the purpose of safety and security.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The usage of Expedia can also improve the gratification of travel. It provides the perspective alternatives relied on city distance, cost and accessibility of hotel and hostels. The excellent part of Expedia is based on offering discounted offers to selected members.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Another important aspect of travel planning is the carrying cash. Few students don&rsquo;t carry some money and mostly relying on debit or credit cards specifically when living in the UK. The majority of students do not know the countries that can accept mu credit or debit cards. Prior to leaving the UK, it is better to have at least about $100 in cash to mitigate any sort of emergency or occasion where money is required.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Utilise each perspective and discount opportunity. Tons of discounts are available, and few experiences such as museum and experiences are offering a reduced rate for students. If the option of the student is not presented to you, the student can inquire about the availability of an opportunity. The places are intended for the accommodation of students. The hostels must have tons of ticket discounts for the mainstream of travel experience and result in the win-win situation. During travel abroad, a student can utilise the option of Public Transportation. It recognised as the smaller manner of saving money, specifically Ubers and taxis are considered as the expensive option and don&rsquo;t consider as worthwhile. The Business and Metro are regarded as the secure manner for engagement with people and another member of society in the short run and ensure the living as the local citizen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The students can also consult with any Travel Agency to gain information about any discounted fares. It is indispensable to obtain an International Student Identity Card. The students will be surprised to see the abundant opportunities of student card and some are also sighting for the group based on discounted offers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The overseas students can enjoy the fun-loving and free things across entire Europe. It is advised to inquire about the private information about tourist specifically by considering an event calendar as major EU cities are offering summer festive, exhibits, concerts and more. The majority of cities are offering free events for the general public in the same instant along with steeping discounts for interested students. The student can look for the scheduled event that provides fun and anything free. A large number of European sites are effectively attracting the young people crowd, and it is fun to have free acrobats, jugglers, painters and others aspects that have offered any sort of high-quality entertainment. Plenty of information is available about many festivities across Europe and even planning their trips for visiting such festivals for the guaranteed and assured time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Overall, I believed that travelling to foreign places, for instance, learning from my mistakes of travel and gain experience of diverse culture and interaction with people belonging to different part of the world can be perceived as the most rewarding and eye-catching experience during overseas studying.</p>', 1, 8, 'published', 'how-to-plan-your-travel-while-in-study', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 18:38:13', '2018-10-01 18:38:13', NULL);
