(79, 'Scholarship', '<p>A scholarship is considered as the main instrument to encourage and inspire the students towards further education. In general, scholarship is provided to college/university education, technical and research expertise and others. The significance of Scholarship is more prominent for different institutes of education and government. The sponsors are interested keenly because of hidden advantages. The educational scholarship offers the additional funds to help out the enrollment of students. For the perspective of sponsors, the scholarship resulted in goodwill, fame among the public in addition to the tax advantage for the government.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Here are the chief benefits of Scholarship in the context of international education in the UK:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Aid in Higher Education:</strong> It provides the opportunity for international students to gain higher education devoid of any reliance on the student loan. The UK and other developed states are providing ample fellowship for postgraduates and PhD programs and strengthen the process of acquisition of higher education and boost up the overall academic progress.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Support the Improved Performance</strong>: The Scholarship enables the students for demonstration of excellent performance. As a basic compulsion is that students can continue the fellowship on the basis of previous semester performance.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Research &amp; Development</strong>: After completion of the college degree, a large number of students can opt for employment and minimally interested in research-based projects. However, progress at an existing level and development of technology require greater research need. The different scholarship provision allows the students to opt for research in diverse fields.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>An attraction of Foreign Students</strong>: the Scholarship provides the manner for an attraction of students from overseas students. It is also noticed that a large number of students are capable of competing for the improved universities in the UK. It is quite challenging to imagine about the well-reputed universities that are enrolling a majority of talented students. The few countries students are far better in specific subjects as compared to native students. Hence, the imbibing of talented and capable students across the globe is probably because of improved scholarship.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Augmentation in Collaboration &amp; Research:</strong> The few students are participating in innovative initiatives of student exchange program among diverse nations. It also provides the manner for enhancing the lab collaboration and ensures the accessibility of resources. For the government level, the research collaboration provides the roadmap to attain improved technology and expert human capital.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The UK based Universities are categorized as the leading and world-class worthwhile universities. The international educational sector of UL has incorporated superior quality and flexible education. The Quality education comes up with greater charges and preliminary studies in the UK are highly expensive unless students opt for scholarship and same opportunities for funding. As the universities of UK are persistently ranked as the divine institution in all over the world with the high value on the international level, hence, a scholarship of UK have greatly sought after. The acquisition of degree from reputed universities of UK will aid the success of career for the international student. The UK based scholarships are generally awarded to those students that are duly meeting the eligibility criteria.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The most prevailing UK based scholarship for worldwide students are discussed below:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Cambridge University Scholarship:</strong> The University is offering the different type of scholarship for global students and one prominent initiative is based on Gates Cambridge scholarship. This scholarship is offered by entire academic excellence. The university is well regulated by the Higher Education Council for Funding in the UK. The level of scholarship is offered for Masters and PhD students.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Chevening Scholarship:</strong> This type of scholarship is based on an international award program in UK and aimed for the deliverance of the worldwide leader. The foreign and commonwealth is responsible for funding this type of scholarship. It is mostly offered for Master study level.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>British Council IELTS:</strong> This type of scholarship is offered to British Councils to peruse the Bachelors and Masters in any discipline. It is based on partial scholarship with worth range of &pound;3,000 to of &pound;10,000 maximum level. It is open to all nations and can be taken at any time.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Skoll Scholarship &amp; Brilliant Mind:</strong> This type of scholarship is offered with full funding in addition to a stipend for living till the completion of MBA. The brilliant mind scholarship is provided by Imperial Business College to peruse the MBA and based on fractional funds with the value of &pound;23,500.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; According to a statement of great Nelson Mandela;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>&ldquo;The acquisition of education is the sole way to get rid of poverty. It is pleaded by the entire government specifically those students that belong to developing nations for a reintroduction of national and international schemes of scholarship. It provides support to young students for perusing their education for becoming excellent leaders in the future. The government is required to invest for the sustainable future in education and scholarship provision is just the novel manner to achieve this objective&rdquo;.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is also argued that due to increasing cost of university living that includes meal plans, books, on campus housing that lead to addition of huge bucks in entire semester charges. In this sense, the availing the opportunities for scholarship can be used for offsetting the increased and place the student mind at ease for the overall semester.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The organization and institutions offering scholarship to students should take care for accurate management of finances to assure about the maintenance of powerful relation with recipient and donors.&nbsp; A contemporary technique is based on implementation of scholar management software as the effective manner for monitoring of scholarship related activities. The Scholarship provides the opportunities to diverse people for earning an education and without support of external resource, student would have trouble to pay for their academic degree requirement for entrance in workforce and ensue the contribution as the society members. A Scholarship Software Management Plan enables the streamlining of process acceptance for strengthening the critical association, founded with donors. It also provides the assurance for following policies regarding the allocation of funds as well as distribution. It is helpful for creation of reports with the help of recorded information and effectively demonstrates about the effectively powered scholarship having on entire student community.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 8, 'published', 'scholarship', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 18:39:57', '2018-10-01 18:39:57', NULL),
(80, 'Some Effective Tips for Writing a Successful MBA Application Essay', '<h1>Some Effective Tips for Writing a Successful MBA Application Essay</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>For the students, it is one of the most crucial elements to decide whether they are the right candidate or not for applying. The top-ranked business schools want from the applicant to submit their MBA essays in their part of the application process. The writing of MBA essay is helpful to stand out from the fierce competition and arguments that provide chances to get admission in favorite business school. The application essays are useful in giving the opportunities in order to highlight the strengths and explanation of the story and expertise to the admission committee directly. The MBA application essays must be original, attention-getting and must be represented as the best. The applicants can get benefits from the excellent opportunity and end up writing the poor application essays. It is helpful to assist with application essay writing that is by searching for the services and consultants offering professional MBA essay samples. The writer must focus on the success of the essay writing. It is successful by using examples provided by the prestigious essay writing services. The services are helping the students in preparing the strategies and learning different things they need to consider while writing MBA essays as the part of their application process. The applicant must choose the consultant agency that offers the application essay samples and professional editing services at affordable prices. However, it is better to write an application essay on their own. The writer must take note of the question that is asked and answer it carefully and thoroughly. The key points are having to share with the users. The student must provide the information about why he is going to apply for the particular program.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The essay is considered as the crucial phase in the application process of MBA. The people are selecting a committee to read and getting to know the candidates for their potential. The writing reveals and remains hidden for the mechanical stages of the examinations. It is essential to stay bright, competent, and useful in the essay writing. The writing involves personal elements that are viewed and controlled the ways of showing the person to the committee. It is helpful to display the strengths and emphasize on the achievements in order to be humble. Its proven that the excellent essay merely is the achievements of the ultimate goals to convince the admission committee belongs to the business school. The essay must accomplish fundamental things like answering the questions to be asked and making the clear and precise points that are well written. Moreover, for achieving the excellent essays, it is helpful to demonstrate the senses and targets for the adequate representation. The applicant must provide valuable assets for the program with the use of unique qualities, experiences, attributes, and background. Therefore, the essays are arguably for the critical elements of the MBA applications. These are subjective in nature and potentially provide the edge to the admission process. The essays are helpful for developing the MBA applications and controlled by the students through test scores, grades and recommendations.</p>', 1, 8, 'published', 'some-effective-tips-for-writing-a-successful-mba-application-essay-1', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 18:40:56', '2018-10-01 18:40:56', NULL),
(81, 'Some Tips to Write an Essay Winningly', '<h1>Some Tips to Write an Essay Winningly</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>In order to write an essay that is successful and qualitative, it is essential for the writer to organize the thoughts. It is helpful to see connections and links between the ideas more clearly while heading the words into the papers. The structure serves as the foundation of the paper. It is useful for outlining the diagram, jot downing it to the ideas, and organizes it. The thesis statements have two parts. In which the first part states the topic and the second part indicates the point of the essay. All the knowledge in the world is providing rhetorical skills in order to express the knowledge fluently and succinctly. To write a brilliant and original essay, it is essential to meet all the assignment brief that is likely to frustrate the waste of the efforts. It may get the sufficient credit for the originality in the work. The student can achieve more marks by writing more originally and accurately. One of the best ways to pay attention is by two things like the content of the quality sources the student found in the studies and the rhetoric styles used in the sources employed in writing. The writer must frame the arguments in the scholastic ways. Learning of new language is undoubtedly the ambitious and challenging task. There are many small details to learn, and the process is helpful in taking a lot of time to commit. It is useful in practicing and improving the study. The writers must have to find the tips first while writing the essays that will enhance their writing skills and abilities.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The body of the essay must argue, explains, and describes the topic.&nbsp; The main idea is to provide a separate section within the body of the essay. The body must have the same basic structure. It begins with the writing of main ideas as introductory sentence and support ideas in the next sentences. It provides the detailed examples for backing up the position. It is helpful in filling up the relative information that is helpful in linking smaller ideas together. As starting with an introduction, the writer must use shocking details, dialogues, quotes, and a summary of the topic to be described. It is helpful to choose the angels and toes the thesis statements that should be included in the last sentence of the introduction. The conclusion must be closure to the topic that must contain the sum up of overall ideas in order to provide the final perspective on the issue. The outcome must have three to five strong sentences. It is considered the review of the main points in the essay that reinforce the thesis. The reading is also an important thing while writing. It goes towards the sayings that to know what is going to write about. The writer must have the reading list and have time to read the material before writing an essay. It is better to look into the stance that list and figures the books based on the titles, blurb, and on the list of the contents.</p>', 1, 8, 'published', 'some-tips-to-write-an-essay-winningly-1', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 18:44:14', '2018-10-01 18:44:14', NULL),
(82, 'Telling the Importance of Essay Writing', '<p>The essays play an essential part in the academic writing that contains the arguments of the author. The word essay itself has it&#39;s variously used that describe different kinds in the academic paper. The philosophers and scholars provided the work essay as their works as like essay writing. However, nowadays, the term essay is used to describe the short academic writing on a particular topic that is the teaching to the students. Essay writing is essential to provide the avenue of the thoughts of the writer. It is the tackling of the personal opinion about the specific subject. It is written to perceive things accordingly. It is helpful in providing the critical thinking abilities to the essay writing tasks. The writing on argumentative essay topics is required in order to give the excellent sense of criticizing subjects and issues that are important to think on. The essay writing is helpful in discovering more knowledge by doing some researching. The students may relate the topics of the essay that are probably required to research, and it is possible to create new information about the innocent topic ideas. Essay writing provides the chances to the students and to the writers to improve their skills in general. The aspect of essay writing is perfect in spelling and grammar conditions that are helpful in realizing the learning and writing of articles correctly. The essay writing has different levels that always demand the writer to write in the technical ways and the high standards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The essay writing is essential for the students in their higher studies by demonstrating the abilities to decode the complex subject matters. Essay writing on a different and unfamiliar topic is helpful for the students to learn and understand more on difficult academic works. The comprehension is useful in essay writing. The argumentative essays are challenging for the students to write. They have to provide a strong case for the particular point of view as it seems from the personal position of the author. The essay writing is helpful in assisting the organization and modulation of thoughts of the writers. It is easier to find material for writing essays, but the difficulty lies in assembling and arrangement of the material into good essay work. It is useful to create a flow in writing an essay in its art of its own. It involves lots of creativity and intelligence that is important in contributing the intellectual development for the students and helpful to become sharp and organized for academics and daily life. Writing skills are essential in all fields, and the students must be careful in writing their essays. It is necessary for the students to provide better quality because the better presentation is helpful for them in writing and worth reading. Therefore, the students are making their academic writing assignments as good in their investments and their career in order to present the scholarly writing. Thus, essay writing is helpful for the students in improving their skills with appropriate vocabulary and well-organized writing style that help them to express more logical ways of writing.</p>', 1, 8, 'published', 'telling-the-importance-of-essay-writing-1', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 18:45:53', '2018-10-01 18:45:53', NULL),
(83, 'Top 5 Most Effective Communication Techniques and Strategies', '<h1><strong><u>Top 5 Most Effective Communication Techniques and Strategies</u></strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The communication is playing an active role in everyone&rsquo;s life. Effective communication can be utilized in several forms. People are mostly connected with each other through different communication channels. There are following top 5 way for most effective communication technologies and communication.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Ask Questions</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>No matter how able you are, no matter how much you have superior information. You have to ask the question in every way of life. There are two types of question that pertain in the communication process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em><u>Open-ended question:</u></em></strong><strong>&nbsp; </strong>These questions provide a broad way to express the answer of the question with comprehensive detail.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><em><u>Closed-ended questions:</u></em></strong>&nbsp; These questions are designed with limited answers. It could be a good tool to collect the basic information.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Listening</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>The communication will be consider useless when there is lack of effective listening. Listening is not an activity in which you are using your ear to collect the sound. You need to understand and listen properly what is being delivered. Maintain effective listening that helps to focus on other people&rsquo;s capabilities, intentions and motivation.&nbsp; In this way, you can provide the knowledgeable and coherent response to the people. Conferences, classrooms and seminars are the most effective way to improve the listening skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Feedback</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>The important part of the communication is feedback. It pertains on both your intended recipients and from your side. It is very effective to convey the right information so that your target audience can deliver the proper feedback to you. There should be clear feedback on every direct question. Try to convey some information to the people and make it practical to giving and receiving appropriate feedback. It could be the simplest way to get the effective feedback. Do not make the complicated situation for the audience so as to they cannot give you positive feedback. Always deliver the best quality of information so that your partner should be able to offer suitable feedback.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Speak Equally</strong>​​​​​</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Always speak equally with the audience. It shows the best verbal communicator skills. The communicator delivers equal speaking with him or her so that they can understand the presentation was designed especially for them. It is one of the type of communicator&rsquo;s skills to gain attention. Find the best communicator and observe how he or she deliver the information in front of the audience. In that session, you can learn new things and then implement those skills in your communication.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Never Stop Learning</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Sometimes people often make huge mistakes during the learning process of communication. They always think that they are the effective communicator and they know very well about everything. There is nothing left to learn for them. But they forget that learning has no any end.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As there are no any skills are left inn this universe that can replace and remove the ability of effective communication. All of these above techniques and strategies will take lots of time to learn. You cannot even think that you have learned enough. There is always something left that you need to learn more.</p>', 1, 8, 'published', 'top-5-most-effective-communication-techniques-and-strategies-1', 1, 1, 1, '2018-10-01 19:04:09', '2018-10-01 19:04:09', NULL);

